WEBVTT

1
00:00:17.080 --> 00:00:20.550
JUICE BY TAPPY !
JUICE BY TAPPY !
JUICE BY TAPPY !

2
00:00:20.550 --> 00:00:24.060
<i>OHHH. TAPPY'S GOT JUICE !
TAPPY'S GOT JUICE !</i>

3
00:00:24.060 --> 00:00:28.040
<i>OHHH. TAPPY !
[ Cheering ]</i>

4
00:00:28.040 --> 00:00:31.530
<i>[ Tappy ]
JUICE !  JUICE !  JUICE !</i>

5
00:00:31.530 --> 00:00:33.530
<i>JUICE BY YOU !
 JUICE BY YOU !</i>

6
00:00:33.530 --> 00:00:39.040
<i>JUICE !  JUICE BY YOU !
THANK YOU. THANK YOU. THANK YOU.</i>

7
00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:42.040
<i>[ Man ]  WE GOT A WINNER.
[ Audience ]
WE GOT A WINNER !</i>

8
00:00:42.040 --> 00:00:44.540
<i>I SAID. WE GOT A WINNER.
WE GOT A WINNER !</i>

9
00:00:44.540 --> 00:00:46.540
<i>WE GOT A WINNER.
WE GOT A WINNER !</i>

10
00:00:46.550 --> 00:00:49.560
<i>OUR FIRST WINNER
IS A FLIGHT ATTENDANT
FROM WASHINGTON. D.C.</i>

11
00:00:49.550 --> 00:00:52.050
<i>PLEASE WELCOME MARY KELLINGTON.</i>

12
00:00:52.050 --> 00:00:56.050
<i>[ Audience ]
JUICE BY MARY !
JUICE BY MARY !  OHHH--</i>

13
00:00:56.060 --> 00:00:59.070
- [ Man Pulls Plug Out ]
- HAROLD. PLEASE.
  NOT AGAIN THE TV.

14
00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:04.060
MA !  COME ON. MA !
WHY DO YOU HAVE TO MAKE
A BIG DEAL OUTTA THIS ?

15
00:01:04.060 --> 00:01:07.570
YOU KNOW YOU'LL GET
THE SET BACK
IN A COUPLE OF HOURS.

16
00:01:09.070 --> 00:01:12.570
WHY YA GOTTA MAKE ME
FEEL SO GUILTY ?

17
00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:21.080
JESUS !
WHAT ARE YOU TRYING TO DO ?

18
00:01:21.080 --> 00:01:25.080
<i>TRYING TO GET ME TO BREAK
MY OWN MOTHER'S SET ?
OR BREAK THE RADIATOR ?</i>

19
00:01:25.080 --> 00:01:28.590
<i>AND MAYBE BLOW UP
THE HOUSE ?  IS THAT WHAT
YOU'RE TRYING TO DO ?</i>

20
00:01:28.590 --> 00:01:34.590
YOUR OWN FLESH AND BLOOD !
IS THAT WHAT YOU'RE TRYING
TO DO ?  YOUR OWN SON ?

21
00:01:34.590 --> 00:01:38.100
WHY DO YOU ALWAYS GOTTA
PLAY GAMES WITH MY HEAD.
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE ?

22
00:01:38.100 --> 00:01:41.600
<i>HAROLD.
I WOULDN'T DO THAT.</i>

23
00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:45.100
THE CHAIN ISN'T FOR YOU.
IT'S FOR THE ROBBERS.

24
00:01:45.100 --> 00:01:48.610
THEN WHY WON'T YOU
COME OUT ?

25
00:01:48.610 --> 00:01:52.110
[ Rattles Door ]

26
00:01:52.110 --> 00:01:56.610
SEE WHAT I MEAN ?
SEE HOW YOU ALWAYS GOTTA
UPSET ME. MA ?

27
00:01:56.620 --> 00:01:58.630
CHRIST'S SAKE.

28
00:02:06.630 --> 00:02:09.140
[ Sighs ]

29
00:02:10.130 --> 00:02:12.630
MA ?

30
00:02:13.630 --> 00:02:15.630
MA !

31
00:02:18.140 --> 00:02:20.640
COME ON OUT.
PLEASE. MA ?

32
00:02:23.140 --> 00:02:26.140
AH. SCREW IT !

33
00:02:26.150 --> 00:02:29.160
THIS ISN'T HAPPENING.

34
00:02:29.650 --> 00:02:33.150
AND IF IT SHOULD BE HAPPENING.
IT WOULD BE ALL RIGHT.

35
00:02:33.150 --> 00:02:37.660
SO DON'T WORRY. SEYMOUR.
IT'LL ALL WORK OUT.

36
00:02:37.660 --> 00:02:41.660
YOU'LL SEE ALREADY.
IN THE END. IT'S ALL NICE.

37
00:02:47.150 --> 00:02:51.650
SHIT. MAN.
THAT MOTHERFUCKER'S STARTING
TO LOOK A LITTLE SEEDY.

38
00:02:51.650 --> 00:02:53.660
WHAT. ARE YOU PARTICULAR
ALL OF A SUDDEN ?

39
00:02:53.660 --> 00:02:58.660
I DON'T CARE IF
THE MOTHERFUCKER'S GROWING HAIR.
AS LONG AS WE GET OUR BREAD.

40
00:02:58.660 --> 00:03:01.160
JUST GIVE ME A HAND.
TYRONE.

41
00:03:07.670 --> 00:03:11.170
- HELLO.
- [ Together ]  HI.

42
00:05:16.300 --> 00:05:17.800
WHOOPIE FUCK.
THE TABLE TOO !

43
00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:21.300
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME ?
YOU WANT ME TO SCHLEP IT
ON MY BACK ?

44
00:05:21.300 --> 00:05:25.310
- YOU GOT A FRIEND.
- I AIN'T MY LEPER'S SCHLEPPER.
  SHIT.

45
00:05:25.310 --> 00:05:30.810
SUCH A SON.  A GONIFF !
YOUR MOTHER NEEDS YOU LIKE
A MOOSE NEEDS A HAT RACK.

46
00:05:36.820 --> 00:05:39.320
♪ [ Rock ]

47
00:05:39.320 --> 00:05:42.820
♪

48
00:05:42.830 --> 00:05:45.840
[ Laughing ]

49
00:05:46.830 --> 00:05:49.330
♪ [ Music Stops ]

50
00:05:49.330 --> 00:05:51.830
♪ [ Rock ]

51
00:05:51.830 --> 00:05:56.840
♪

52
00:05:56.840 --> 00:06:01.840
SHIT. MAN.
THIS IS SOME BOSS SCAG.

53
00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:05.850
I MEAN. DYNAMITE.
OH. MAN.
IT'S SOMETHING ELSE.

54
00:06:11.350 --> 00:06:13.860
YOU KNOW WHAT
WE NEED TO DO ?

55
00:06:15.860 --> 00:06:19.860
WE NEED TO GET US
A PIECE OF THIS BRODY SHIT.
CUT IT UP AND OFF IT !

56
00:06:19.860 --> 00:06:22.360
WE COULD DOUBLE OUR MONEY...
EASY.

57
00:06:22.870 --> 00:06:25.880
WE COULD BUY US A COUPLE
OF PIECES. AND WE GOT SOME
WHOLE OTHER SHIT GOING ON.

58
00:06:26.370 --> 00:06:27.870
THAT'D BE RIGHTEOUS.

59
00:06:27.870 --> 00:06:33.880
I'LL BET IN NO TIME WE'D GET
A POUND OF PURE STRAIGHT
FROM SAL THE GEEP.

60
00:06:33.880 --> 00:06:38.380
OOOH !  THAT'S WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT.
NO HASSLES.

61
00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:45.390
- <i>HOW'S IT GOIN' ?  THE USUAL ?
</i>- WHAT'S UP. BUDDY ?
  YEAH. SOUNDS GOOD.

62
00:07:21.420 --> 00:07:23.930
ANYTHING ELSE ?  HUH ?

63
00:07:25.430 --> 00:07:29.430
- <i>[ Waiter ]  ANYTHING ELSE ?
</i>- AH. NO.

64
00:07:29.930 --> 00:07:31.930
NOTHING.
I'M ALL RIGHT.

65
00:07:39.940 --> 00:07:43.950
<i>- GOOD AFTERNOON. MRS. GOLDFARB.
- GOOD AFTERNOON.
  MR. RABINOWITZ.</i>

66
00:07:43.950 --> 00:07:46.950
ALTHOUGH I'M NOT SO SURE
HOW GOOD IT IS.
AND YOU ?

67
00:07:46.950 --> 00:07:50.950
- WHAT CAN I SAY ?
  YOU WANT YOUR TV ?
- YES. IF YOU DON'T MIND.

68
00:07:52.460 --> 00:07:54.970
MRS. GOLDFARB.
CAN I ASK YOU A QUESTION ?

69
00:07:55.460 --> 00:07:57.960
YOU WON'T TAKE IT PERSONAL ?

70
00:07:57.960 --> 00:08:01.460
HOW MANY YEARS
WE KNOW EACH OTHER ?
WHO'S TO COUNT ?

71
00:08:01.460 --> 00:08:05.470
WHY DON'T YOU TELL ALREADY
THE POLICE ?  MAYBE THEY
COULD TALK TO HARRY.

72
00:08:05.470 --> 00:08:10.470
<i>HE WOULDN'T BE STEALING
     NO MORE THE TV.
</i>I COULDN'T DO THAT.

73
00:08:10.470 --> 00:08:13.980
HARRY'S MY ONLY CHILD.
HE'S ALL I HAVE.

74
00:08:13.980 --> 00:08:16.980
THANK YOU.
MR. RABINOWITZ.

75
00:08:16.980 --> 00:08:21.980
- [ Padlock Locks ]
- JOIN US IN CREATING
  EXCELLENCE.  JUICE !

76
00:08:23.990 --> 00:08:27.490
<i>[ TV ]
YOU HAVE MORE PASSION FOR LIVING
THAN YOU'VE EVER IMAGINED.</i>

77
00:08:27.490 --> 00:08:30.490
<i>[ Audience On TV ]
BE EXCITED !
BE. BE EXCITED !</i>

78
00:08:30.490 --> 00:08:33.490
<i>BE EXCITED !
 BE. BE EXCITED !</i>

79
00:08:33.500 --> 00:08:36.510
<i>BE EXCITED !
 BE. BE EXCITED !</i>

80
00:08:36.500 --> 00:08:39.500
<i>BE EXCITED !
 BE. BE EXCITED !</i>

81
00:08:39.500 --> 00:08:42.500
<i>[ TV Continues Indistinct ]</i>

82
00:09:12.540 --> 00:09:16.550
- <i>[ Old Man ]
  HELLO ?  WHO IS IT ?
</i>- [ Mumbling ]

83
00:09:16.540 --> 00:09:18.540
<i>[ Buzzer Buzzes ]</i>

84
00:09:25.550 --> 00:09:28.050
[ Elevator Bell Rings ]

85
00:09:31.050 --> 00:09:34.060
- <i>AW. SHIT.
</i>- NOW WHAT ?

86
00:09:43.070 --> 00:09:46.080
[ Phone Ringing ]

87
00:09:47.570 --> 00:09:50.070
[ Ringing Continues ]

88
00:09:57.580 --> 00:10:01.080
HELLO ?
[ Man ]  MRS. GOLDFARB ?
MRS. SARA GOLDFARB ?

89
00:10:01.080 --> 00:10:05.090
- ME.  SPEAKING.
- THIS IS LYLE RUSSEL
  FROM MAYLIN AND BLOCK.

90
00:10:05.090 --> 00:10:08.590
I'M NOT INTERESTED--
    WAIT.  I'M NOT SELLING
    ANYTHING.  NOTHING.

91
00:10:08.590 --> 00:10:13.090
<i>I JUST WANT TO OFFER YOU
A CHANCE
TO BE ON TELEVISION.</i>

92
00:10:13.100 --> 00:10:18.610
TELEVISION ?
THAT'S RIGHT. TELEVISION.
CONGRATULATIONS !

93
00:10:18.600 --> 00:10:21.600
LOOK. I DON'T HAVE ANY--
I'M NOT LOOKING FOR MONEY.
MRS. GOLDFARB.

94
00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:24.610
I'M CALLING TO TELL YOU
YOU'VE ALREADY WON.

95
00:10:24.610 --> 00:10:28.610
MAYLIN AND BLOCK DISCOVERS
CONTESTANTS FOR MOST
OF AMERICA'S TELEVISION SHOWS.

96
00:10:28.610 --> 00:10:32.610
YOU'VE ALREADY BEEN CHOSEN
FROM A LONG LIST
OF POTENTIAL CONTESTANTS.

97
00:10:32.620 --> 00:10:35.130
<i>MEANING.
YOU'VE ALREADY WON.</i>

98
00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:40.120
YES. MRS. GOLDFARB.
I NEVER THOUGHT I'D BE
ON TELEVISION.  I'M JUST--

99
00:10:40.120 --> 00:10:42.120
THAT'S RIGHT.
YOU ON TELEVISION.

100
00:10:42.630 --> 00:10:45.140
WE'LL BE SENDING YOU ALL
THE NECESSARY INFORMATION
IN THE MAIL.

101
00:10:45.130 --> 00:10:48.630
GOOD-BYE. CONGRATULATIONS
AND TAKE CARE.

102
00:11:36.680 --> 00:11:39.180
[ Sighs ]

103
00:11:54.700 --> 00:11:59.200
<i>[ Harry ]  I DON'T GET IT.
WHY ARE YOU
SO HARD ON YOUR FOLKS ?</i>

104
00:11:59.200 --> 00:12:02.200
<i>I MEAN.
THEY GIVE YOU EVERYTHING.</i>

105
00:12:02.200 --> 00:12:05.210
<i>THEY HOOK YOU UP
WITH AN APARTMENT.
WITH A CROAKER SHRINK.</i>

106
00:12:05.210 --> 00:12:09.710
WHICH IS FINE. YOU KNOW.
IT'S GREAT.  IT'S JUST--

107
00:12:10.210 --> 00:12:13.210
MONEY IS NEVER WHAT I REALLY
WANTED FROM THEM. YOU KNOW.

108
00:12:13.220 --> 00:12:16.730
THAT'S PRETTY MUCH ALL
THEY HAVE TO GIVE.

109
00:12:16.720 --> 00:12:19.720
<i>[ Harry ]
WHY DON'T YOU
GET AWAY FROM 'EM ?</i>

110
00:12:19.720 --> 00:12:22.220
<i>[ Marion ]
HOW AM I GONNA DO THAT ?</i>

111
00:12:22.220 --> 00:12:26.730
I DON'T KNOW.
WHAT ABOUT YOUR CLOTHES ?

112
00:12:26.730 --> 00:12:30.230
<i>YOUR SKETCHES ARE GREAT.
OPEN UP A STORE.</i>

113
00:12:30.230 --> 00:12:32.230
I CAN'T.

114
00:12:32.740 --> 00:12:37.250
- WHY NOT ?
- WHEN WILL I HAVE TIME
  TO HANG WITH YOU ?

115
00:12:49.250 --> 00:12:52.250
WELL !
SO WHERE'S THE PARTY ?

116
00:12:52.250 --> 00:12:54.260
WHEN I TELL YOU. YOU'RE
GONNA JUMP OUTTA THE WINDOW.

117
00:12:58.760 --> 00:13:01.260
[ Mumbling ]

118
00:13:05.770 --> 00:13:08.270
I GOT A GREAT DIET BOOK.

119
00:13:10.270 --> 00:13:12.270
HEY.

120
00:13:14.280 --> 00:13:17.280
[ Buzzer. Alarm Blaring ]

121
00:13:22.790 --> 00:13:25.300
THEY'RE COMING.

122
00:13:41.800 --> 00:13:45.060
[ Laughing ]

123
00:13:47.810 --> 00:13:50.810
BE EXCITED !
 BE. BE EXCITED !

124
00:13:50.810 --> 00:13:54.320
<i>[ Chanting Continues ]</i>

125
00:14:58.380 --> 00:15:02.380
I THOUGHT I'D CATCH
A LITTLE SUN TODAY.

126
00:15:02.380 --> 00:15:05.390
REALLY ?  WELL. IN A BOX
YOU'LL CATCH IT.

127
00:15:05.390 --> 00:15:10.390
RELAX AND THINK HOW
GORGEOUS YOU'LL LOOK
WITH YOUR NEW RED HAIR.

128
00:15:10.390 --> 00:15:13.890
TODAY THE HAIR.
TOMORROW THE SUN.

129
00:15:15.400 --> 00:15:17.900
ANYBODY WANT
TO WASTE SOME TIME ?

130
00:15:21.900 --> 00:15:24.910
<i>[ Harry's Voice ]
ANGEL SAYS THAT THIS IS
THE TIME. WE SHOULD DO IT NOW.</i>

131
00:15:24.910 --> 00:15:26.910
<i>[ Tyrone's Voice ]
I'M GONNA CALL BRODY TOMORROW.
[ Marion's Voice ] WHO'S BRODY ?</i>

132
00:15:26.910 --> 00:15:30.410
<i>[ Tyrone ]
THAT'S MY SWEET CONNECTION.
HE'S GOT UNBELIEVABLE SHIT.</i>

133
00:15:30.410 --> 00:15:31.910
<i>[ Tyrone ]
SHIT. RIGHTEOUS.</i>

134
00:15:31.910 --> 00:15:35.420
<i>[ Harry ]
MARION. WE GOT THIS IDEA.
WHAT IS IT ?</i>

135
00:15:35.920 --> 00:15:39.420
<i>IF WE GET A PIECE OF THIS STUFF.
WE CAN CUT IT UP AND
DOUBLE OUR MONEY. NO PROBLEM.</i>

136
00:15:39.420 --> 00:15:44.930
<i>[ Tyrone ]  THEN WE GET A POUND
OF PURE AND RETIRE.  YOU KNOW
WHAT THAT MEANS.  NO MORE HACKS.</i>

137
00:15:44.930 --> 00:15:48.430
<i>[ Harry ]
WE GET OFF HARD KNOCKS
AND BE ON EASY STREET.</i>

138
00:15:48.430 --> 00:15:51.930
WHAT'S THE CATCH ?

139
00:15:51.930 --> 00:15:55.440
THAT'S A RED.
I MEAN. THAT'S A RED.

140
00:15:55.440 --> 00:15:58.940
IT'S NOT A RED RED.
BUT THAT'S A RED.
IT'S A RED.

141
00:15:58.940 --> 00:16:00.940
RED ?
        YEAH.
        IT'S A RED.

142
00:16:00.940 --> 00:16:04.450
YOU'RE TELLING ME
THAT'S RED ?
    YEAH. I'M TELLING YOU.

143
00:16:04.450 --> 00:16:09.950
THEN WHAT'S ORANGE ?
IF THIS IS A RED.
I WANT TO KNOW WHAT'S ORANGE ?

144
00:16:12.960 --> 00:16:17.970
WELL. IT COULD BE...

145
00:16:17.960 --> 00:16:21.460
THAT IT'S
A LITTLE ORANGE TOO.

146
00:16:23.470 --> 00:16:26.980
YOU KNOW SOMETHING ?
                        HMM ?

147
00:16:31.970 --> 00:16:36.480
I ALWAYS THOUGHT YOU WERE
THE MOST BEAUTIFUL GIRL
I'VE EVER SEEN.

148
00:16:36.480 --> 00:16:38.480
REALLY ?

149
00:16:43.490 --> 00:16:46.500
EVER SINCE I FIRST SAW YOU.

150
00:16:46.490 --> 00:16:48.990
THAT'S NICE. HARRY.

151
00:16:54.500 --> 00:16:58.000
MAKES ME FEEL REALLY GOOD.

152
00:17:00.500 --> 00:17:03.000
OTHER PEOPLE HAVE TOLD ME
THAT BEFORE.

153
00:17:03.010 --> 00:17:06.020
AND IT WAS MEANINGLESS.

154
00:17:13.020 --> 00:17:18.030
WHY ?
BECAUSE YOU THOUGHT
THEY WERE PULLING YOUR LEG ?

155
00:17:18.520 --> 00:17:22.020
NO. NO.
NOT LIKE THAT.

156
00:17:22.020 --> 00:17:25.530
I DON'T KNOW.
I DON'T KNOW OR EVEN CARE
IF THEY WERE.

157
00:17:25.530 --> 00:17:28.530
JUST FROM THEM
IT WAS...

158
00:17:30.030 --> 00:17:33.530
JUST MEANINGLESS.
YOU KNOW ?

159
00:17:34.540 --> 00:17:39.040
WHEN YOU SAY IT.
I HEAR IT.

160
00:17:40.040 --> 00:17:43.040
I REALLY HEAR IT.

161
00:17:48.550 --> 00:17:53.050
SOMEBODY LIKE YOU
COULD REALLY MAKE THINGS
ALL RIGHT FOR ME.

162
00:17:53.060 --> 00:17:55.070
YOU THINK ?

163
00:17:57.560 --> 00:17:59.560
<i>[ Marion ]
WHAT IS IT ?</i>

164
00:17:59.560 --> 00:18:02.560
<i>[ Harry ]
REMEMBER WHEN I TOLD YOU
ABOUT THE STORE ?</i>

165
00:18:02.560 --> 00:18:04.570
YEAH.

166
00:18:04.570 --> 00:18:06.570
I'VE BEEN THINKING
ABOUT IT A LOT.

167
00:18:06.570 --> 00:18:10.070
<i>I PUT TOGETHER
SOME NUMBERS.</i>

168
00:18:10.070 --> 00:18:12.570
AND IT'S NOT IMPOSSIBLE !

169
00:18:13.580 --> 00:18:16.090
I MEAN. YOU KNOW.
YOU COULD DO IT.

170
00:18:16.080 --> 00:18:19.080
<i>YOU SHOULD DO IT !</i>

171
00:18:19.080 --> 00:18:21.080
WE COULD DO IT TOGETHER.

172
00:18:27.590 --> 00:18:29.590
WHAT DO YOU THINK ?

173
00:19:33.160 --> 00:19:36.670
[ Stomach Growling ]
STOP ALREADY.

174
00:19:36.660 --> 00:19:40.660
YOU'LL FEEL BETTER
IN THE RED DRESS
THAN IN THE CHEESE DANISH.

175
00:20:17.200 --> 00:20:19.700
THREE THINGS IS ALL I DID
TO CHANGE MY LIFE.
THREE THINGS.

176
00:20:20.200 --> 00:20:22.700
[ Audience ]
NUMBER ONE !
NO RED MEAT !

177
00:20:22.700 --> 00:20:25.710
<i>THINK ABOUT IT.
WHAT DO THEY STICK IN RED MEAT ?</i>

178
00:20:25.710 --> 00:20:28.710
<i>I ATE RED MEAT TO THE POINT
WHERE I WOULD EAT IT...</i>

179
00:20:28.710 --> 00:20:30.710
<i>SLAB. RIGHT OFF. RAW.</i>

180
00:20:30.710 --> 00:20:32.710
<i>I LOVED MY MEAT !
 I TURNED IT AROUND.</i>

181
00:20:32.710 --> 00:20:36.220
<i>YOU NEED TO BE COMMITTED.
YOU NEED TO BE PASSIONATE.
NO RED MEAT.</i>

182
00:20:36.220 --> 00:20:40.220
<i>NO RED MEAT FOR 30 DAYS.
 NO RED MEAT !</i>

183
00:20:40.220 --> 00:20:44.220
<i>THREE THINGS IS ALL I DID
TO CHANGE MY LIFE.
THREE THINGS.</i>

184
00:20:55.240 --> 00:20:57.740
ADA TOLD US.
IT'S GORGEOUS.

185
00:20:57.740 --> 00:20:59.740
WE'RE GONNA MAKE IT
A LITTLE DARKER TOMORROW.

186
00:21:00.240 --> 00:21:02.240
- WHY DARKER ?
- TO GO WITH MY RED DRESS.

187
00:21:02.240 --> 00:21:05.250
- YEAH. BUT NOW IT'S
  LOOKING LIKE MADONNA.
- THIS IS NOT MADONNA.

188
00:21:05.250 --> 00:21:08.750
AND NEITHER IS THIS.
BUT SOON.  I'M GOING ON A DIET.

189
00:21:08.750 --> 00:21:11.250
- WHAT DIET ARE YOU ON ?
- EGGS AND GRAPEFRUIT.

190
00:21:11.250 --> 00:21:14.250
- I WAS ON THAT ONE.
  LOTS OF LUCK.
- IT'S NOT SO BAD.

191
00:21:14.260 --> 00:21:16.770
- <i>HOW LONG YOU BEEN ON IT ?
</i>- ALL DAY.

192
00:21:16.760 --> 00:21:21.260
- ALL DAY !  IT'S 1:00 !
  [ Laughing ]
- [ Laughing ]

193
00:21:21.260 --> 00:21:23.760
- I'M THINKING THIN.
- SHE'S THINKING THIN.

194
00:21:23.770 --> 00:21:27.280
MY LOUISE. SHE LOST 50 POUNDS
JUST LIKE THAT.

195
00:21:27.270 --> 00:21:28.770
- LIKE THAT ?
- LIKE WHAT ?
- POOF !

196
00:21:29.270 --> 00:21:32.270
- WHAT'D YOU DO ?
  PUT HER IN A SWEATBOX ?
- [ Laughing ]

197
00:21:32.270 --> 00:21:36.280
SHE WENT TO A DOCTOR.
HE GAVE HER PILLS.
YOU DON'T WANT TO EAT.

198
00:21:36.780 --> 00:21:38.280
<i>SO ?
WHAT'S SO GOOD ABOUT THAT ?</i>

199
00:21:38.280 --> 00:21:42.280
<i>YOU MEAN. I'M SITTING HERE
NOT THINKING ABOUT CHOPPED LIVER
AND PASTRAMI ON RYE ?</i>

200
00:21:42.280 --> 00:21:45.290
YOU KNOW. YOU REALLY
SHOULDN'T TALK LIKE THAT
WHEN SOMEONE'S ON A DIET.

201
00:21:45.290 --> 00:21:48.790
OH. BIG DEAL.
I'LL SNEAK ANOTHER WEDGE
OF GRAPEFRUIT.

202
00:21:50.790 --> 00:21:54.800
- I'M THINKING THIN !
- SARA. THE MAILMAN.

203
00:21:54.800 --> 00:21:59.800
SARA GOLDFARB.  YOU HAVE
SOMETHING FOR SARA GOLDFARB ?
I'M EXPECTING SOMETHING.

204
00:21:59.800 --> 00:22:03.300
GOLDFARB. GOLDFARB.
SARA GOLDFARB.

205
00:22:03.310 --> 00:22:05.820
<i>IS THAT IT ?
        </i>THAT'S IT !

206
00:22:05.810 --> 00:22:08.310
COME ON.
    WAIT. I GOTTA GET MY STUFF.

207
00:22:08.310 --> 00:22:12.810
ALL RIGHT. I CAN TELL YOU.
YOUR NAME.

208
00:22:12.810 --> 00:22:16.820
WHAT'S YOUR NAME ?
S-A-R-A G-O-L-D--

209
00:22:16.820 --> 00:22:18.820
[ All ]
F-A-R-B !

210
00:22:19.320 --> 00:22:21.820
DYNAMITE ?
IT'S DYNAMITE.

211
00:22:23.830 --> 00:22:25.840
DYNAMITE !

212
00:22:25.830 --> 00:22:29.330
ALL RIGHT. WE ON OUR WAY.

213
00:22:29.330 --> 00:22:31.330
BRODY'S MAN SAYS
HE GOT SOME REAL FINE SHIT.

214
00:22:31.330 --> 00:22:33.830
ALL RIGHT. MAN.

215
00:22:33.840 --> 00:22:37.350
- HERE WE GO.
- TY ?

216
00:22:37.340 --> 00:22:39.840
LET'S DO THIS RIGHT. MAN.

217
00:22:39.840 --> 00:22:42.340
COME ON. BABY.
NATURALLY.

218
00:22:45.350 --> 00:22:49.350
HURRY. HURRY.
        LET'S HURRY.
I WONDER WHEN YOU'LL HEAR.

219
00:22:50.850 --> 00:22:53.850
HI !
<i>[ Woman ]
I WANNA COME WITH YOU !</i>

220
00:22:53.860 --> 00:22:56.370
MAYBE THEY'LL SEND YOU
TO THE TAVERN ON THE GREEN.

221
00:22:56.360 --> 00:22:58.360
THAT'S WHERE THEY SEND
ALL THE STARS.

222
00:22:58.860 --> 00:23:01.860
YEAH. I'M EATING EGGS
AND GRAPEFRUIT
AT TAVERN ON THE GREEN.

223
00:23:01.860 --> 00:23:04.360
I HOPE THEY HAVE THAT.
            HURRY BEFORE
            THE MAILMAN COMES.

224
00:23:04.370 --> 00:23:06.380
HERE WE ARE.
                MAIL IT !

225
00:23:08.370 --> 00:23:12.370
[ Woman ]
OH. SARA !

226
00:23:12.370 --> 00:23:15.880
[ Woman ]
THIS IS SO EXCITING !
 THIS IS SO EXCITING !

227
00:24:22.440 --> 00:24:25.950
- <i>THERE IT IS. JIM.
</i>- HUH ?

228
00:24:26.950 --> 00:24:30.950
- THERE IT IS. BABY.
- SHIT !

229
00:24:30.950 --> 00:24:35.460
- SHALL WE TRY IT ?
- WAIT. TY.

230
00:24:35.460 --> 00:24:40.460
LOOK. THIS IS OUR CHANCE
TO MAKE IT BIG.

231
00:24:40.460 --> 00:24:45.970
WE PLAY IT RIGHT.
 WE CAN GET A POUND OF PURE.

232
00:24:45.970 --> 00:24:49.970
<i>BUT IF WE GET WASTED.
WE'LL FUCK IT UP.</i>

233
00:24:49.970 --> 00:24:55.480
I KNOW.
HEY. LOOK. I AIN'T TRYING
TO JIVE YOU. JIM.

234
00:24:55.480 --> 00:25:00.980
I DON'T WANNA BE RUNNING THE
STREETS. MY SNEAKERS RIPPED UP.
MY NOSE RUNNIN' DOWN TO MY CHIN.

235
00:25:00.980 --> 00:25:04.990
ALL I'M SAYIN' IS
WE SHOULD TAKE A LITTLE TASTE
SO WE KNOW HOW MUCH TO CUT.

236
00:25:04.990 --> 00:25:06.990
IT'S BUSINESS.

237
00:25:08.990 --> 00:25:10.990
FAIR ENOUGH.

238
00:25:17.500 --> 00:25:21.000
SHIT !
[ Laughing ]

239
00:25:37.020 --> 00:25:41.520
THANK YOU !
THREE THINGS IS ALL I DID.
THIRTY DAYS IS ALL IT TAKES.

240
00:25:41.520 --> 00:25:44.520
NUMBER TWO !
NO REFINED SUGAR !

241
00:25:44.530 --> 00:25:47.040
<i>NOW. SUGAR'S EVERYWHERE.</i>

242
00:25:47.030 --> 00:25:50.530
<i>YOU KNOW THEY EVEN PUT SUGAR
IN BOTTLED WATER ?</i>

243
00:25:50.530 --> 00:25:53.530
<i>I WAS SICK WITH SUGAR !
THAT WAS MY MEDICINE.</i>

244
00:25:53.540 --> 00:25:58.550
IT NURTURED ME.
IT NURTURED MY SPIRALLING BRAIN
THAT FELT I WAS A LOSER.

245
00:25:59.040 --> 00:26:03.540
<i>[ Audience ]
JUICE BY YOU !
RULE TWO IS NO REFINED SUGAR.</i>

246
00:26:04.050 --> 00:26:07.060
<i>SODAS ?  DON'T EVEN THINK
ABOUT SODAS ANYMORE.</i>

247
00:26:07.050 --> 00:26:11.050
NO SUCKING CANDIES.
NONE OF THAT STUFF.
JUST STAY AWAY FROM IT.

248
00:26:12.550 --> 00:26:15.560
<i>NO REFINED SUGAR.
WATCH IT FOR 30 DAYS.</i>

249
00:26:15.560 --> 00:26:18.060
<i>I'M GONNA EAT RIGHT.</i>

250
00:26:18.560 --> 00:26:21.560
I AM GONNA PICK UP MY SPIRITS.
AND I AM GONNA TRY !

251
00:26:21.560 --> 00:26:26.070
<i>I FOUND HOPE.
AND IN THAT HOPE.
I FOUND A WAY--</i>

252
00:26:33.580 --> 00:26:36.090
SHUT UP !

253
00:27:11.110 --> 00:27:12.610
[ Woman ]
HELLO ?
    ROSIE ?

254
00:27:13.110 --> 00:27:15.120
YEAH.
    SARA.

255
00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:17.620
I NEED THE NUMBER
OF THAT DOCTOR.

256
00:27:20.120 --> 00:27:22.620
<i>[ Harry ]
I DON'T UNDERSTAND
WHY YOU GOTTA SEE HIM.</i>

257
00:27:22.620 --> 00:27:25.630
CUT THE SON OF A BITCH LOOSE.
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE.

258
00:27:25.630 --> 00:27:29.630
BECAUSE I DON'T WANT HIM
MENTIONING TO MY PARENTS
THAT I'VE STOPPED THERAPY.

259
00:27:29.630 --> 00:27:33.130
<i>THEY'RE ALREADY SO PISSED OFF
AT ME THEY'RE THINKING
OF CUTTING ME OFF. YOU KNOW.</i>

260
00:27:33.640 --> 00:27:36.650
<i>HARRY. I'M NOT GONNA SLEEP
WITH HIM OR ANYTHING.</i>

261
00:27:36.640 --> 00:27:40.140
I'M GONNA COME HOME
AFTER THE CONCERT.

262
00:27:40.140 --> 00:27:43.640
YOU'RE JEALOUS !

263
00:27:43.650 --> 00:27:46.160
HARRY JEALOUS ?

264
00:27:47.150 --> 00:27:50.650
PUT YOUR ARMS
    AROUND ME.
NO.

265
00:27:50.650 --> 00:27:54.650
YOU ARE SO STUBBORN !
PUT YOUR ARMS AROUND ME.

266
00:27:56.660 --> 00:27:58.660
STOP THAT !

267
00:27:59.160 --> 00:28:01.660
I'LL SUCK
            YOUR EYEBALLS OUT.
MM-HMM.

268
00:28:01.660 --> 00:28:04.660
WELL--

269
00:28:05.170 --> 00:28:07.670
I'M DISAPPOINTED
THAT YOU'RE INDISPOSED.

270
00:28:10.170 --> 00:28:12.170
IS ANITA OUT OF TOWN
OR SOMETHING ?

271
00:28:12.170 --> 00:28:15.180
WHY DO YOU ASK ?

272
00:28:15.180 --> 00:28:18.680
I WAS JUST WONDERING
IF SHE WAS "INDISPOSED."

273
00:28:23.180 --> 00:28:24.680
<i>NO.</i>

274
00:28:24.690 --> 00:28:29.200
SHE'S FINE. THANK YOU.
ACTUALLY. SHE'S IN FLORIDA.

275
00:28:29.190 --> 00:28:33.190
- CAN I ASK YOU
  SOMETHING PERSONAL. ARNOLD ?
- OF COURSE.

276
00:28:37.200 --> 00:28:39.700
- ANYTHING.  WHAT ?
- I--  YOU JUST HAVE
  SOMETHING OVER HERE.

277
00:28:40.200 --> 00:28:44.200
- GONE ?
- A LITTLE BIT.
  A LITTLE BIT LOWER.

278
00:28:44.710 --> 00:28:47.220
IT'S OKAY.
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
IT'S MUCH BETTER.

279
00:28:47.210 --> 00:28:49.210
ARNOLD !

280
00:28:51.710 --> 00:28:54.210
HOW ARE YOU.
MRS. GOLDFARB ?

281
00:28:54.220 --> 00:28:57.730
HOW AM I ?  ENORMOUS.
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.

282
00:28:57.720 --> 00:29:01.720
I'VE SEEN MUCH WORSE.
            OH... THANK YOU.

283
00:29:01.720 --> 00:29:05.230
HOW'S YOUR HEARING
AND VISION ?
                I HAVE BOTH.

284
00:29:06.730 --> 00:29:09.230
THE DOCTOR WILL BE WITH YOU
SHORTLY.

285
00:29:16.740 --> 00:29:19.240
I SEE YOU'RE
A LITTLE OVERWEIGHT.
                 <i>A LITTLE ?</i>

286
00:29:19.240 --> 00:29:22.240
I HAVE 50 POUNDS
I'M WILLING TO DONATE.

287
00:29:22.240 --> 00:29:25.250
WE CAN TAKE CARE OF THAT.
NO PROBLEM.

288
00:30:15.300 --> 00:30:17.300
WE'RE ON OUR WAY. BABY.

289
00:30:17.300 --> 00:30:19.800
<i>WE ARE ON OUR WAY !</i>

290
00:30:19.800 --> 00:30:23.300
<i>IT WAS GREAT OUT THERE.
I MEAN.
EVERYBODY IS THIRSTY.</i>

291
00:30:23.300 --> 00:30:27.310
COME TO ME.
[ Laughing ]

292
00:30:27.310 --> 00:30:31.310
HARRY !
I AM SO GLAD.

293
00:30:36.320 --> 00:30:38.320
<i>[ Man ]
NATURALLY.</i>

294
00:30:41.820 --> 00:30:43.820
<i>[ Man ]
NATURALLY.</i>

295
00:30:48.830 --> 00:30:50.830
<i>[ Man ]
NATURALLY.</i>

296
00:31:13.860 --> 00:31:16.870
PURPLE IN THE MORNING.

297
00:31:16.860 --> 00:31:20.860
BLUE IN THE AFTERNOON.
ORANGE IN THE EVENING.

298
00:31:21.860 --> 00:31:25.370
<i>THERE'S MY THREE MEALS.
MR. SMARTY PANTS.</i>

299
00:31:26.870 --> 00:31:29.870
AND GREEN AT NIGHT.
JUST LIKE THAT.

300
00:31:29.870 --> 00:31:32.370
ONE. TWO. THREE. FOUR.

301
00:31:54.400 --> 00:31:58.910
<i>♪ [ Rhythmic ]</i>

302
00:31:58.900 --> 00:32:12.410
♪

303
00:32:15.920 --> 00:32:20.920
<i>[ Man On TV Speaking Faster ]</i>

304
00:32:41.940 --> 00:32:43.940
WHY DON'T YOU COME BACK
TO BED. BABY ?

305
00:32:43.950 --> 00:32:47.960
COME ON NOW. ALICE.
GOT PLENTY OF TIME FOR THAT.

306
00:32:47.950 --> 00:32:50.950
RIGHT NOW I'M GROOVING
WITH THESE NEW MIRRORS I GOT.

307
00:32:50.950 --> 00:32:52.950
OOOH !

308
00:33:11.970 --> 00:33:15.980
I TOLD YA. MOM.
ONE DAY I'D MAKE IT.

309
00:33:15.980 --> 00:33:17.980
YOU DON'T HAVE
TO MAKE ANYTHING. MY SWEET.

310
00:33:17.980 --> 00:33:20.480
YOU JUST HAVE TO LOVE
YOUR MAMA.

311
00:33:20.480 --> 00:33:23.480
<i>[ Alice ]
WHAT YA DOIN'. BABY ?</i>

312
00:33:23.480 --> 00:33:25.490
HUH ?
<i>WHAT YA DOIN' ?</i>

313
00:33:25.490 --> 00:33:27.490
NOTHIN'.

314
00:33:30.990 --> 00:33:35.500
JUST THINKIN' ABOUT YOU.

315
00:33:35.500 --> 00:33:38.000
ABOUT THE NASTY THINGS
I'M ABOUT TO DO TO YA.

316
00:33:38.000 --> 00:33:40.500
[ Laughs ]
    I'M GONNA GET ON YOU !

317
00:33:41.000 --> 00:33:43.500
[ Laughing ]

318
00:33:43.500 --> 00:33:45.510
TY. YOU SCARE ME
TO DEATH.

319
00:33:45.510 --> 00:33:50.510
NO. I WOULDN'T SCARE YOU.
I DON'T WANNA SCARE NOBODY.

320
00:33:53.010 --> 00:33:57.520
ALL I WANT OUT OF LIFE
IS A LITTLE BIT OF PEACE
AND HAPPINESS.  THAT'S ALL.

321
00:33:57.520 --> 00:34:01.020
RIGHT NOW.

322
00:34:01.020 --> 00:34:05.020
YOU'RE THE FINEST FOX
I EVER LAID MY EYES ON.

323
00:34:06.530 --> 00:34:09.530
[ Harry ]
THAT'S WHAT I'LL DO.
[ Marion ]  HMM ?

324
00:34:10.030 --> 00:34:13.530
FOR MY MOTHER.
I'VE BEEN THINKING ABOUT
GETTING SOMETHING FOR HER.

325
00:34:13.530 --> 00:34:16.540
LIKE... LIKE A PRESENT
OR SOMETHING.

326
00:34:16.540 --> 00:34:21.040
BUT I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT
I WAS GONNA GET.
UNTIL NOW.
                AND ?

327
00:34:21.040 --> 00:34:24.040
I FINALLY ASKED MYSELF.
RIGHT. WHAT'S HER FIX ?

328
00:34:25.550 --> 00:34:27.550
TELEVISION. RIGHT ?

329
00:34:27.550 --> 00:34:30.550
<i>IF EVER THERE'S
A TV JUNKIE.
IT'S THE OLD LADY.</i>

330
00:34:30.550 --> 00:34:33.550
<i>I FIGURE I OWE HER
A NEW SET ANYWAY. WITH ALL
THE WEAR AND TEAR IT GOT...</i>

331
00:34:33.550 --> 00:34:37.560
FROM BEING SCHLEPPED BACK
AND FORTH TO OLD ABE'S
ALL THE TIME.

332
00:34:37.560 --> 00:34:39.560
YOU REALLY LOVE HER.
DON'T YOU ?

333
00:34:42.560 --> 00:34:44.560
I. I GUESS SO.
YOU KNOW ?

334
00:34:48.070 --> 00:34:50.570
MOST OF THE TIME
I JUST WANT HER TO BE HAPPY.

335
00:34:51.070 --> 00:34:54.570
LET'S GO GET IT NOW.

336
00:34:54.580 --> 00:34:56.590
LET'S PUSH-OFF FIRST.

337
00:34:58.080 --> 00:35:00.580
[ Marion Laughs ]

338
00:35:00.580 --> 00:35:03.580
IT'S EARLY. HARRY.
WE SHOULDN'T GET GOING
TILL TONIGHT.

339
00:35:51.130 --> 00:35:54.130
BE EXCITED.
 BE. BE EXCITED.

340
00:35:54.140 --> 00:35:58.150
<i>BE EXCITED.
 BE. BE EXCITED.</i>

341
00:35:58.140 --> 00:36:00.640
YOU NEED TO BE COMMITTED.
 YOU NEED TO BE PASSIONATE.

342
00:36:00.640 --> 00:36:06.650
<i>I AM A LIVING TESTAMENT.
SIXTY-FIVE POUNDS THINNER.
I FEEL GREAT !</i>

343
00:36:14.660 --> 00:36:16.170
- NUMBER THREE.
- [ Audience ]  THREE !

344
00:36:16.160 --> 00:36:20.160
<i>OHHH. NUMBER THREE !</i>

345
00:36:20.160 --> 00:36:23.160
[ Speaking Very Slowly ]
THIS DRIVES PEOPLE CRAZY.

346
00:36:26.170 --> 00:36:29.670
THIS IS EASY SO FAR.
[ Voice Continues Slowed Down ]

347
00:37:22.720 --> 00:37:27.730
<i>[ Ada ]
THAT IS THIN !  SHE DOESN'T LOOK
LIKE THE SAME PERSON.</i>

348
00:37:27.730 --> 00:37:31.230
I CAN ALMOST ZIP--
THE RED DRESS ?
I'VE ALMOST GOT THE ZIPPER UP.

349
00:37:31.230 --> 00:37:33.230
THE MAILMAN !

350
00:37:33.230 --> 00:37:35.740
MRS. GOLDFARB.
WHEN I SEE IT. I'M GONNA
WAVE IT ALL OVER THE PLACE.

351
00:37:35.740 --> 00:37:38.740
ARE YOU SURE ?
YEAH. I'M SURE.

352
00:37:38.740 --> 00:37:42.240
WHAT DID HE SAY ?
DON'T WORRY. SARA.
IT'LL COME.

353
00:37:42.240 --> 00:37:44.740
<i>YEAH. DON'T WORRY.
IT'LL COME.</i>

354
00:37:47.750 --> 00:37:50.750
IT'S HARRY !
HARRY. OH !

355
00:37:50.750 --> 00:37:55.250
HEY. MA. EASY.
YOU'LL CRUSH ME.
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE.

356
00:37:55.260 --> 00:37:58.270
COME INSIDE.
            HI. HARRY !

357
00:37:58.260 --> 00:38:01.260
HELLO. HARRY !
[ Sara ]
WE'LL HAVE A LITTLE VISIT.

358
00:38:01.260 --> 00:38:04.760
SO. HOW ARE YOU. HARRY ?
YOU'RE LOOKING SO GOOD.

359
00:38:04.770 --> 00:38:06.780
YOU WANT SOMETHING
TO EAT ?
                NO. MA.

360
00:38:06.770 --> 00:38:11.270
<i>A LITTLE NOSH MAYBE.
A PIECE OF CAKE ?  I COULD
GO OUT AND GET SOMETHING.</i>

361
00:38:11.270 --> 00:38:14.770
I DON'T HAVE ANYTHING
IN THE HOUSE.
BUT ADA WOULD HAVE SOMETHING.

362
00:38:14.780 --> 00:38:17.290
A CUPCAKE ?
YOU WANT SOMETHING TO EAT ?

363
00:38:17.280 --> 00:38:20.280
NO. NO. MA. NOTHING.
PLEASE SIT.

364
00:38:20.280 --> 00:38:23.280
YOU'RE MAKING ME DIZZY.
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE.

365
00:38:23.280 --> 00:38:26.790
YOU NOTICE ANYTHING
ABOUT ME. HUH ?
YOU NOTICE I'M SLIMMER ?

366
00:38:27.290 --> 00:38:29.290
YEAH. I GUESS YOU ARE.

367
00:38:29.290 --> 00:38:32.790
TWENTY-FIVE POUNDS. I LOST.
TWENTY-FIVE POUNDS !
CAN YOU BELIEVE IT ?

368
00:38:32.790 --> 00:38:36.300
<i>AND THAT'S ONLY THE BEGINNING.
        </i>THAT'S GREAT. MA.
         THAT'S REALLY GREAT.

369
00:38:36.300 --> 00:38:40.800
I'M REALLY HAPPY FOR YOU.
BUT WILL YOU SIT ?  PLEASE.

370
00:38:43.800 --> 00:38:48.310
I'M SORRY I HAVEN'T
BEEN AROUND IN A WHILE. MA.
BUT I'VE BEEN BUSY.

371
00:38:48.310 --> 00:38:51.310
OH. YEAH ?
YOU GOT A GOOD JOB ?
YOU'RE DOING REAL WELL ?

372
00:38:51.310 --> 00:38:54.310
- YEAH. REAL GOOD. REAL GOOD.
- WHAT KIND OF BUSINESS ?

373
00:38:54.820 --> 00:38:59.330
WELL. I'M SORT OF
A DISTRIBUTOR LIKE.
FOR A BIG IMPORTER.

374
00:38:59.320 --> 00:39:01.820
OHHHH !
I'M SO HAPPY FOR YOU !

375
00:39:01.820 --> 00:39:04.320
EASY.
YOU'RE KILLIN' ME.

376
00:39:04.330 --> 00:39:06.840
JESUS. YOU BEEN
LIFTING WEIGHTS ?

377
00:39:06.830 --> 00:39:09.830
- I ALWAYS KNEW
  YOU COULD DO THAT.
- YOU WERE RIGHT.

378
00:39:09.830 --> 00:39:13.330
NOW MAYBE YOU'LL MEET
A NICE GIRL AND HAVE A BABY ?

379
00:39:14.840 --> 00:39:16.850
WELL. I ALREADY MET ONE.

380
00:39:16.840 --> 00:39:19.840
[ Squealing ]
        MA. DON'T.
        DON'T GO APE SHIT.

381
00:39:19.840 --> 00:39:22.840
SO WHO IS SHE ?
WHO'S HER PARENTS ?
            YOU KNOW HER.

382
00:39:22.840 --> 00:39:24.840
MARION ?
MARION SILVER.
REMEMBER ?

383
00:39:24.850 --> 00:39:29.860
OH. SILVER !  OF COURSE.
MANHATTAN BEACH.

384
00:39:30.350 --> 00:39:33.350
<i>HE'S GOT A HOUSE
ON THE ESPLANADE.
GARMENT BUSINESS.</i>

385
00:39:33.350 --> 00:39:35.350
YEAH. HE'S REAL BIG
IN WOMEN'S UNDIES.

386
00:39:35.860 --> 00:39:40.360
BEFORE YOU GO BOUNCING
ALL OVER AGAIN
AND MAKE ME FORGET. JUST--

387
00:39:41.860 --> 00:39:45.360
WHAT I WANNA TELL
YOU IS THAT
I GOT YOU A PRESENT.

388
00:39:45.370 --> 00:39:48.380
I DON'T NEED A PRESENT.
JUST HAVE A BABY.

389
00:39:48.370 --> 00:39:53.370
WILL YOU LET ME TELL YOU
WHAT I GOT YA ?
WILL YA. MA ?

390
00:39:53.370 --> 00:39:57.880
CHRIST. YOU ARE REALLY
SOMETHING ELSE TODAY.
YOU KNOW THAT ?

391
00:39:57.880 --> 00:40:03.380
<i>LOOK. I KNOW--
WELL--</i>

392
00:40:04.890 --> 00:40:09.400
I'M SORRY FOR BEING
SUCH A BASTARD.
I WANNA MAKE IT UP.

393
00:40:09.890 --> 00:40:13.890
<i>I MEAN. I KNOW I CAN'T
CHANGE ANYTHING
THAT'S HAPPENED.</i>

394
00:40:13.890 --> 00:40:15.900
BUT I WANT YOU
TO KNOW...

395
00:40:15.900 --> 00:40:19.900
THAT I LOVE YA.
AND THAT I'M SORRY.

396
00:40:21.900 --> 00:40:25.910
AND I WANT YOU TO BE HAPPY.
SO I GOT YOU
A BRAND-NEW TV SET.

397
00:40:25.910 --> 00:40:29.910
IT'S GONNA BE DELIVERED
IN A COUPLE OF DAYS.
IT'S FROM MACY'S !

398
00:40:29.910 --> 00:40:31.910
OH. HARRY !

399
00:40:33.910 --> 00:40:39.420
YOUR FATHER'D BE SO HAPPY
IF HE COULD SEE WHAT
YOU'RE DOING FOR YOUR MOTHER.

400
00:40:43.420 --> 00:40:45.420
SEE THAT. SEYMOUR ?

401
00:40:45.430 --> 00:40:48.440
YOU SEE HOW GOOD YOUR SON IS ?

402
00:40:48.430 --> 00:40:52.430
HE KNOWS WHAT IT'S LIKE
FOR HIS MOTHER
LIVING ALL ALONE.

403
00:40:52.430 --> 00:40:54.930
<i>NO ONE TO VISIT HER.</i>

404
00:40:54.940 --> 00:40:56.950
<i>[ Grinding Sound ]</i>

405
00:41:04.450 --> 00:41:06.960
- [ Grinding Sound ]
- HEY. MA !

406
00:41:07.950 --> 00:41:10.450
- YOU ON UPPERS ?
- WHAT ?

407
00:41:10.450 --> 00:41:14.450
YOU'RE ON UPPERS !
YOU'RE ON DIET PILLS.
AIN'T YOU ?

408
00:41:14.460 --> 00:41:16.970
I TOLD YOU.
I'M GOING TO A SPECIALIST.

409
00:41:16.960 --> 00:41:20.460
THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT !
YOU'RE MAKING A CROAKER
FOR SPEED. AIN'T YA ?

410
00:41:20.460 --> 00:41:22.960
HARRY. ARE YOU ALL RIGHT ?
I'M GOIN' TO A DOCTOR.

411
00:41:22.960 --> 00:41:26.470
- DOES HE GIVE YOU PILLS ?
- OF COURSE HE GIVES ME PILLS.
  HE'S A DOCTOR.

412
00:41:26.470 --> 00:41:29.470
- WHAT KIND OF PILLS ?
- A PURPLE ONE. A BLUE ONE.
  AN ORANGE ONE--

413
00:41:29.970 --> 00:41:31.470
I MEAN. LIKE
WHAT'S IN 'EM ?

414
00:41:31.970 --> 00:41:36.480
OH. HARRY. I'M SARA GOLDFARB.
NOT ALBERT EINSTEIN.
HOW SHOULD I KNOW ?

415
00:41:36.980 --> 00:41:39.480
DOES THE STUFF MAKE YOU
FEEL GOOD. SORT OF.
AND GIVE YOU LOTS OF PEP ?

416
00:41:39.980 --> 00:41:41.980
OH... YEAH. A LITTLE.

417
00:41:42.480 --> 00:41:44.480
A LITTLE ?
MA. I CAN HEAR YA GRINDING
YOUR TEETH FROM HERE.

418
00:41:44.990 --> 00:41:46.500
THAT GOES AWAY AT NIGHT.

419
00:41:46.490 --> 00:41:48.490
AT NIGHT ?
YEAH. WHEN I TAKE
THE GREEN ONE.

420
00:41:48.490 --> 00:41:51.990
<i>THIRTY MINUTES I'M ASLEEP.
POOF. JUST LIKE THAT.</i>

421
00:41:51.990 --> 00:41:57.500
MA. MA. YA GOTTA CUT
THAT STUFF LOOSE.
IT'S NO GOOD.

422
00:41:57.500 --> 00:42:00.500
WHAT DO YOU MEAN IT'S NO GOOD ?
TWENTY-FIVE POUNDS I'VE LOST.

423
00:42:00.500 --> 00:42:03.000
BIG DEAL !  SO WHAT ?
YOU WANNA BE A DOPE FIEND.
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE ?

424
00:42:03.000 --> 00:42:07.510
WHAT IS WITH THIS DOPE FIEND ?
AM I FOAMING AT THE MOUTH ?
HE'S A NICE DOCTOR.

425
00:42:07.510 --> 00:42:10.010
I AM TELLING YOU
THAT CROAKER'S NO GOOD.

426
00:42:10.010 --> 00:42:14.010
HOW COME YOU KNOW SO MUCH. HUH ?
HOW COME YOU KNOW MORE
ABOUT MEDICINE THAN A DOCTOR ?

427
00:42:16.020 --> 00:42:20.020
BELIEVE ME. MA. I KNOW.
ALL RIGHT ?

428
00:42:20.020 --> 00:42:23.020
YOU'LL GET STRUNG OUT.
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE.

429
00:42:23.020 --> 00:42:26.030
COME ON !
I ALMOST FIT IN MY RED DRESS.

430
00:42:26.030 --> 00:42:29.530
THE ONE I WORE
TO YOUR HIGH SCHOOL GRADUATION.

431
00:42:29.530 --> 00:42:31.530
THE ONE
YOUR FATHER LIKED SO MUCH.

432
00:42:31.530 --> 00:42:37.540
I REMEMBER HOW HE LOOKED
AT ME IN THAT RED DRESS.

433
00:42:37.540 --> 00:42:39.540
WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL
ABOUT THE RED DRESS ?

434
00:42:43.040 --> 00:42:48.550
I'M GOING TO WEAR THE--
OH. YOU DON'T KNOW !

435
00:42:48.550 --> 00:42:53.050
I'M GONNA BE ON TELEVISION.
I GOT A CALL
AND AN APPLICATION AND--

436
00:42:53.550 --> 00:42:56.060
COME ON. MA.
WHO'S PULLING YOUR LEG ?

437
00:42:56.560 --> 00:42:58.060
NO. NO. NO.
I'M TELLIN' YA.

438
00:42:58.560 --> 00:43:01.560
I'M GONNA BE A CONTESTANT
ON TELEVISION.

439
00:43:01.560 --> 00:43:04.060
I DON'T KNOW WHEN YET.
THEY HAVEN'T TOLD ME YET.

440
00:43:04.060 --> 00:43:07.070
BUT YOU'LL SEE HOW PROUD YOU ARE
WHEN YOU SEE YOUR MOTHER
IN HER RED DRESS...

441
00:43:07.070 --> 00:43:11.070
ON TELEVISION IN GOLDEN SHOES.
     <i>WHAT IS THE BIG DEAL
     ABOUT BEING ON TELEVISION ?</i>

442
00:43:11.570 --> 00:43:14.570
THOSE PILLS WILL KILL YOU
BEFORE YOU EVER GET ON.
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE.

443
00:43:14.580 --> 00:43:16.590
BIG DEAL ?

444
00:43:16.580 --> 00:43:19.080
YOU DROVE UP IN A CAB.

445
00:43:19.080 --> 00:43:22.080
DID YOU SEE WHO HAD
THE BEST SEAT ?

446
00:43:22.080 --> 00:43:27.090
I'M SOMEBODY NOW. HARRY.
EVERYBODY LIKES ME.

447
00:43:27.090 --> 00:43:29.590
<i>SOON...</i>

448
00:43:29.590 --> 00:43:33.590
MILLIONS OF PEOPLE WILL SEE ME
AND THEY'LL ALL LIKE ME.

449
00:43:33.590 --> 00:43:38.100
I'LL TELL THEM ABOUT YOU
AND YOUR FATHER.

450
00:43:38.100 --> 00:43:41.600
HOW GOOD HE WAS TO US.
REMEMBER ?

451
00:43:45.110 --> 00:43:48.620
IT'S A REASON TO GET UP
IN THE MORNING.

452
00:43:49.110 --> 00:43:53.610
IT'S A REASON TO LOSE WEIGHT.
TO FIT IN THE RED DRESS.

453
00:43:55.120 --> 00:43:58.130
IT'S A REASON TO SMILE.

454
00:43:59.120 --> 00:44:02.120
IT MAKES TOMORROW ALL RIGHT.

455
00:44:04.630 --> 00:44:07.140
<i>[ Sighs ]
WHAT HAVE I GOT. HARRY ?</i>

456
00:44:07.130 --> 00:44:09.630
HMM ?

457
00:44:09.630 --> 00:44:13.630
WHY SHOULD I EVEN MAKE THE BED
OR WASH THE DISHES ?

458
00:44:13.630 --> 00:44:18.640
I DO THEM. BUT WHY SHOULD I ?

459
00:44:18.640 --> 00:44:21.140
I'M ALONE !

460
00:44:21.140 --> 00:44:25.140
YOUR FATHER'S GONE.
YOU'RE GONE.

461
00:44:27.150 --> 00:44:29.650
<i>I GOT NO ONE...</i>

462
00:44:29.650 --> 00:44:32.150
TO CARE FOR.

463
00:44:32.150 --> 00:44:35.150
WHAT HAVE I GOT. HARRY ?

464
00:44:39.660 --> 00:44:41.660
I'M LONELY.

465
00:44:43.660 --> 00:44:46.170
I'M OLD.

466
00:44:46.170 --> 00:44:48.670
<i>YOU GOT FRIENDS. MA.</i>

467
00:44:48.670 --> 00:44:51.670
IT'S NOT THE SAME.

468
00:44:51.670 --> 00:44:54.670
THEY DON'T NEED ME.

469
00:44:58.680 --> 00:45:03.180
I LIKE THE WAY I FEEL.

470
00:45:03.180 --> 00:45:05.680
I LIKE THINKING
ABOUT THE RED DRESS...

471
00:45:05.690 --> 00:45:11.200
AND THE TELEVISION
 AND YOU AND YOUR FATHER.

472
00:45:11.190 --> 00:45:15.190
NOW WHEN I GET THE SUN.
I SMILE.

473
00:45:20.200 --> 00:45:22.700
I'LL COME AND VISIT. MA.

474
00:45:24.710 --> 00:45:28.720
NOW THAT I'M STRAIGHT.
MY BUSINESS IS GOING GOOD.
I'LL COME.

475
00:45:28.710 --> 00:45:31.210
ME AND MARION.
WE'LL COME FOR DINNER.

476
00:45:31.210 --> 00:45:33.210
GOOD.
YOU BRING HER.

477
00:45:33.210 --> 00:45:36.720
I'LL MAKE YOU MUSHROOM SOUP
AND A ROAST.

478
00:45:36.720 --> 00:45:40.720
THAT SOUNDS GREAT. MA.
 THAT SOUNDS GREAT.

479
00:45:40.720 --> 00:45:45.220
I'LL GIVE YA A CALL
AHEAD OF TIME. ALL RIGHT ?
                        OKAY.

480
00:45:46.230 --> 00:45:48.230
I'M GLAD.

481
00:45:48.230 --> 00:45:53.730
I'M GLAD YOU HAVE
A NICE GIRL AND YOUR
OWN BUSINESS.  I'M GLAD.

482
00:45:59.740 --> 00:46:04.240
I'VE GOTTA GO. MA.
I GOT AN APPOINTMENT
IN MANHATTAN IN A LITTLE BIT.

483
00:46:04.240 --> 00:46:06.250
BUT I'LL BE BACK.

484
00:46:06.250 --> 00:46:10.250
OKAY. YOU.
        YOU STILL GOT YOUR KEY ?
YEAH. I GOT IT. MA.

485
00:46:12.250 --> 00:46:14.250
BYE. SON.

486
00:46:14.250 --> 00:46:16.260
<i>[ Door Closes ]</i>

487
00:46:26.770 --> 00:46:28.770
[ Sighs ]

488
00:46:34.780 --> 00:46:37.290
[ Crying ]

489
00:46:51.780 --> 00:46:54.290
<i>BRODY SAYS YOU COMIN' UP QUICK.
KID.</i>

490
00:46:54.280 --> 00:46:57.780
OH.  THANKS. MAN.

491
00:47:00.280 --> 00:47:02.780
<i>HE SAYS YOU'RE SMART.
YOU'RE LOYAL.</i>

492
00:47:02.790 --> 00:47:05.300
<i>AND YOU'RE NOT A JUNKIE.</i>

493
00:47:07.790 --> 00:47:09.790
<i>BRODY WANTS TO PROMOTE YOU.</i>

494
00:47:09.790 --> 00:47:12.790
HE WANTS TO GIVE YOU
MORE RESPONSIBILITY.
YOU INTERESTED ?

495
00:47:12.800 --> 00:47:14.810
YEAH. YEAH !

496
00:47:14.800 --> 00:47:17.300
<i>SHIT. YEAH. MAN.</i>

497
00:47:19.300 --> 00:47:21.300
FUCK ME.
I KILL YOU !

498
00:47:21.300 --> 00:47:23.310
BRODY SAYS. YOU FUCK HIM.

499
00:47:23.310 --> 00:47:25.310
<i>"I KILL YOU."
            </i>I GOT THAT.

500
00:47:25.310 --> 00:47:27.310
<i>REMEMBER THAT.</i>

501
00:47:29.810 --> 00:47:31.810
SHIT !
YOU GOT A WHITE DRIVER !

502
00:47:31.820 --> 00:47:33.830
[ Gunshots ]

503
00:47:38.820 --> 00:47:41.320
<i>[ Gunshots ]
</i>FUCK !

504
00:47:43.330 --> 00:47:45.330
WHAT THE FUCK ?
     <i>[ Dog Barking ]</i>

505
00:47:45.330 --> 00:47:48.330
<i>[ Police Siren Wailing ]</i>

506
00:47:54.840 --> 00:47:56.840
<i>DON'T MOVE !</i>

507
00:48:30.370 --> 00:48:32.870
I LOVE YOU. HARRY.

508
00:48:35.380 --> 00:48:39.380
YOU MAKE ME FEEL
LIKE A PERSON.

509
00:48:40.380 --> 00:48:44.890
LIKE I'M ME...

510
00:48:44.890 --> 00:48:47.390
AND I'M BEAUTIFUL.

511
00:48:48.890 --> 00:48:51.390
YOU ARE BEAUTIFUL.

512
00:48:54.900 --> 00:48:58.900
YOU'RE THE MOST
BEAUTIFUL GIRL IN THE WORLD.

513
00:48:59.900 --> 00:49:01.900
YOU'RE MY DREAM.

514
00:49:08.410 --> 00:49:11.910
[ Nurse Over Phone ]
NO. I'M ABSOLUTELY CERTAIN.
I'VE CHECKED AGAIN.

515
00:49:11.920 --> 00:49:14.930
BUT MAYBE YOU GAVE ME
A WEAKER ONE LAST TIME.

516
00:49:14.920 --> 00:49:18.920
THAT ISN'T POSSIBLE.
LIKE I'VE SAID BEFORE.
THEY'RE THE SAME POTENCY.

517
00:49:18.920 --> 00:49:21.420
BUT SOMETHING
ISN'T THE SAME.

518
00:49:21.420 --> 00:49:23.430
YOU'RE JUST BECOMING
ADJUSTED TO THEM.

519
00:49:23.430 --> 00:49:26.430
IT'S NOTHING TO WORRY ABOUT.
MRS. GOLDFARB. OKAY ?

520
00:49:26.430 --> 00:49:28.930
[ Phone Disconnects ]

521
00:49:44.450 --> 00:49:46.950
- WE GOT A WINNER !
- WE GOT A WINNER !

522
00:49:46.950 --> 00:49:51.950
<i>SHE'S A BEAUTIFUL WOMAN
WITH A WINNING SENSE OF HUMOR
AND A MAGICAL SMILE.</i>

523
00:49:51.960 --> 00:49:57.470
FROM BRIGHTON BEACH. BROOKLYN.
LET'S GIVE A JUICY WELCOME
TO MRS. SARA GOLDFARB !

524
00:49:57.460 --> 00:50:00.960
<i>[ Audience ]
JUICE BY SARA !
JUICE BY SARA !</i>

525
00:50:00.960 --> 00:50:03.970
<i>OOOH. SARA !
SARA'S GOT JUICE !
SARA'S GOT JUICE !</i>

526
00:50:03.970 --> 00:50:05.970
OOOH. SARA !

527
00:50:06.470 --> 00:50:09.970
<i>[ Rumbling Noise ]</i>

528
00:50:15.980 --> 00:50:18.980
<i>[ Door Opens ]
[ Guard ]
LOVE. TYRONE C.</i>

529
00:50:18.980 --> 00:50:20.980
<i>GET YOUR SHIT TOGETHER.
YOU MADE BAIL.</i>

530
00:50:20.980 --> 00:50:23.490
HOW MUCH ?

531
00:50:23.490 --> 00:50:26.490
THEY GOT MOST OF OUR CASH.
YOU'RE UP FOR CONSORTIN'.

532
00:50:26.490 --> 00:50:28.490
OH. SHIT. MAN !

533
00:50:28.490 --> 00:50:31.990
<i>ANGEL SAYS THERE'S A WAR
BETWEEN THE ITALIANS
AND THE BLACKS.</i>

534
00:50:32.000 --> 00:50:34.010
SAL THE GEEP
IS KEEPING THE SHIT
DOWN IN FLORIDA...

535
00:50:34.000 --> 00:50:37.500
<i>UNTIL GUYS LIKE BRODY
ARE ALL KNOCKED OFF.
   </i>SHIT.

536
00:50:37.500 --> 00:50:40.500
- NO ONE'S GOT A THING.
- EXCEPT BIG TIM.

537
00:50:40.500 --> 00:50:42.500
LET'S GO SEE HIM.

538
00:50:42.510 --> 00:50:45.520
HE AIN'T SELLIN'.
HE ONLY GIVIN' UP
FOR PUSSY.

539
00:50:45.510 --> 00:50:50.010
- WHAT ?
- PUSSY.  HE'S HOOKED
  ON THE THING. MAN.

540
00:50:50.010 --> 00:50:53.520
<i>I TOLD HIM I'D GIVE HIM
ALL HE WANTS.  HE SAID
I AIN'T CUTE ENOUGH FOR HIM.</i>

541
00:51:06.530 --> 00:51:08.530
<i>[ Tappy On TV ]
COME ON. NUMBER THREE !</i>

542
00:51:08.530 --> 00:51:12.530
<i>THIS DRIVES
MOST PEOPLE CRAZY.</i>

543
00:51:12.540 --> 00:51:14.550
<i>THEY'RE NOT GOING
TO LIKE IT.</i>

544
00:51:14.540 --> 00:51:18.040
<i>THIS IS EASY !
GIVE THIS UP FOR 30 DAYS.
IT WILL.</i>

545
00:51:28.550 --> 00:51:30.550
[ Gasping ]

546
00:51:32.060 --> 00:51:34.070
<i>[ Harry ]
YOU ALL RIGHT ?</i>

547
00:51:36.060 --> 00:51:39.060
YEAH.
IT WAS JUST A BAD DREAM.

548
00:51:40.060 --> 00:51:42.060
<i>WANT SOME WATER ?</i>

549
00:52:03.590 --> 00:52:05.590
MAYBE WE SHOULD
DIP IN NOW.

550
00:52:05.590 --> 00:52:11.090
COME ON !
I ALREADY TOLD YOU. ALL RIGHT ?
IT'S ALL WE HAVE.

551
00:52:11.090 --> 00:52:15.100
TYRONE IS GONNA SCORE
IN THE MORNING. HARRY.

552
00:52:21.100 --> 00:52:23.100
I DON'T KNOW.

553
00:52:23.110 --> 00:52:26.620
<i>IT'S A BITCH OUT THERE.</i>

554
00:52:26.610 --> 00:52:29.110
IT'LL BE OKAY.

555
00:52:30.580 --> 00:52:32.580
IT'LL BE OKAY. HARRY.

556
00:52:36.590 --> 00:52:41.090
[ Sighs ]
YEAH. I GUESS SO.

557
00:52:48.100 --> 00:52:50.100
I LOVE YOU. HARRY.

558
00:52:50.100 --> 00:52:53.100
<i>[ Phone Ringing ]</i>

559
00:52:58.610 --> 00:53:01.110
<i>[ Ringing Continues ]</i>

560
00:53:02.610 --> 00:53:06.620
<i>[ Ringing Slows Down ]</i>

561
00:53:28.640 --> 00:53:32.140
[ Doctor Talking Quickly ]
WHAT SEEMS TO BE THE PROBLEM ?
THE WEIGHT'S DOING FINE.

562
00:53:32.140 --> 00:53:36.140
THE WEIGHT'S FINE.
I'M NOT.

563
00:53:36.150 --> 00:53:38.160
THE REFRIGERATOR--

564
00:53:38.150 --> 00:53:41.150
[ Gasps ]
            SOMETHING WRONG ?

565
00:53:44.150 --> 00:53:46.150
EVERYTHING'S...

566
00:53:49.660 --> 00:53:52.660
ALL MIXED UP.

567
00:53:52.660 --> 00:53:54.660
CONFUSED LIKE.
        THAT'S NOTHING
        TO WORRY ABOUT.

568
00:53:54.660 --> 00:53:58.170
JUST GET THIS FILLED.
MAKE AN APPOINTMENT
FOR A WEEK.

569
00:54:07.180 --> 00:54:08.680
WELL ?

570
00:54:08.680 --> 00:54:12.180
TY AIN'T FOUND NOTHIN'
YET.

571
00:54:13.680 --> 00:54:15.680
WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO ?

572
00:54:15.690 --> 00:54:17.700
I DON'T KNOW.

573
00:54:17.690 --> 00:54:20.690
WELL. YOU HAVE TO DO SOMETHING.

574
00:54:20.690 --> 00:54:24.190
<i>IT'S YOUR FAULT WE DON'T HAVE
SOMETHING FOR THE MORNING.
    </i>WHAT'RE YOU TALKING ABOUT ?

575
00:54:24.190 --> 00:54:28.700
- YOU WERE HOT IN THE BISCUIT
  TO GET OFF LAST NIGHT.
- THAT IS SUCH BULLSHIT !

576
00:54:28.700 --> 00:54:31.200
YOU DIDN'T HAVE TO.
WE COULD'VE HAD SOMETHING NOW.

577
00:54:31.200 --> 00:54:35.200
WHAT WAS I SUPPOSED TO DO ?
SIT AROUND AND WATCH YOU
PUSH OFF AND NOT GO MYSELF ?

578
00:54:35.210 --> 00:54:37.220
DON'T PUT IT ALL
ON ME. OKAY ?

579
00:54:40.710 --> 00:54:42.210
<i>[ Door Slams Shut ]</i>

580
00:54:48.220 --> 00:54:52.720
DON'T WORRY. MAN.
WE'LL FILL IT UP AGAIN.

581
00:54:52.720 --> 00:54:55.220
THINGS'LL GET BETTER.

582
00:54:55.230 --> 00:54:58.240
THEN WE'LL BE FILLIN'
THE BOX BACK UP. YOU KNOW ?

583
00:55:05.240 --> 00:55:08.250
YOU WANNA HEAR THE NEWS ?

584
00:55:08.240 --> 00:55:10.740
WHAT NEWS ?

585
00:55:10.740 --> 00:55:15.240
YOU GOT YOUR GOOD NEWS.
 YOU GOT YOUR BAD NEWS.
SHOOT.

586
00:55:15.250 --> 00:55:17.760
THE GOOD NEWS IS.

587
00:55:17.750 --> 00:55:20.250
COUPLE OF DAYS THERE'S GONNA BE
SOME PRIME BACK ON THE STREET.

588
00:55:20.250 --> 00:55:23.750
- REALLY ?
- MM-HMM.

589
00:55:23.750 --> 00:55:26.250
WHO TOLD YOU THAT ?

590
00:55:26.260 --> 00:55:29.770
ANGEL.
<i>YEAH ?</i>

591
00:55:29.760 --> 00:55:32.760
HE SAYS SAL THE GEEP SENT WORD
TO THE STREETS TO LET
A COUPLE OF KEYS GO...

592
00:55:32.760 --> 00:55:36.260
FOR THE CHRISTMAS SEASON.
HIM BEING A GOOD CHRISTIAN.

593
00:55:36.270 --> 00:55:40.280
<i>NOT WANTIN' ANYBODY TO BE
WANTIN' DURING THIS SEASON.
   </i>YOU BELIEVE IT ?

594
00:55:40.770 --> 00:55:43.770
WELL. I DID.
TILL I HEARD THE BAD NEWS.

595
00:55:43.770 --> 00:55:45.770
<i>[ Footsteps ]</i>

596
00:55:49.280 --> 00:55:51.280
YEAH ?

597
00:55:51.280 --> 00:55:54.280
PRICE IS DOUBLE.
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO COP
FOR WEIGHT.

598
00:55:54.280 --> 00:55:57.790
<i>AT LEAST A HALF
         A PIECE.
</i>HOW MUCH ?

599
00:55:57.790 --> 00:56:01.290
- TWO.
- TWO ?

600
00:56:01.290 --> 00:56:04.290
<i>THAT'S FUCKIN' INSANE !
    </i>WHAT THE FUCK YOU GONNA DO ?

601
00:56:04.290 --> 00:56:06.800
MAN AIN'T GONNA LAY
NO NICKEL BAG ON YA.
THAT'S FOR DAMN SURE.

602
00:56:06.800 --> 00:56:10.800
- WHERE WE GONNA GET TWO ?
- YOU MEAN ARNOLD ?

603
00:56:10.800 --> 00:56:16.300
WELL. YOUR PARENTS
WON'T EVEN RETURN YOUR CALL.

604
00:56:16.310 --> 00:56:18.320
I HAVEN'T SEEN HIM
IN MONTHS.

605
00:56:18.310 --> 00:56:22.310
- SO WHAT ?
  HE'S STILL CALLIN'. AIN'T HE ?
- I DON'T KNOW.

606
00:56:24.310 --> 00:56:26.820
LOOK. I DON'T KNOW
WHAT ELSE TO DO.

607
00:56:26.820 --> 00:56:29.320
<i>THIS IS OUR LAST CHANCE
TO GET BACK ON TRACK !</i>

608
00:56:29.320 --> 00:56:33.320
WE WON'T HAVE TO SCUFFLE
AND MAKE THE FREEZING SCENE
EVERY DAY !

609
00:56:34.820 --> 00:56:37.830
WE NEED THE BREAD.

610
00:56:37.830 --> 00:56:40.830
GETTING THE MONEY
IS NOT THE PROBLEM. HARRY.

611
00:56:40.830 --> 00:56:43.330
WHAT IS THE PROBLEM.
FOR CHRIST SAKE ?

612
00:56:43.330 --> 00:56:46.330
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
I'M GONNA HAVE TO DO TO GET IT.

613
00:56:52.840 --> 00:56:54.840
LOOK.

614
00:56:54.840 --> 00:56:57.850
BABY.

615
00:56:57.850 --> 00:57:01.850
WE'LL BE BACK IN BUSINESS
IN NO TIME.

616
00:57:01.850 --> 00:57:04.850
WE'LL START MOVIN' AGAIN.

617
00:57:04.850 --> 00:57:07.860
AND WE'LL START SAVIN'.

618
00:57:07.860 --> 00:57:10.360
IT'LL BE PERFECT.
JUST LIKE IT WAS.

619
00:57:10.860 --> 00:57:12.860
I PROMISE. MARION.

620
00:57:16.870 --> 00:57:18.870
YOU'LL SEE.

621
00:57:26.380 --> 00:57:28.890
<i>NO. I'VE JUST. UH--</i>

622
00:57:28.880 --> 00:57:33.380
I'VE HAD THIS FLU FOREVER.
IT SEEMS LIKE.

623
00:57:33.380 --> 00:57:36.890
ARE YOU DEPRESSED ?
NO. IT'S NOTHING LIKE THAT.

624
00:57:36.890 --> 00:57:39.890
I'VE BEEN. UH--
 I'VE BEEN REALLY BUSY.

625
00:57:41.390 --> 00:57:44.390
ACTUALLY. I'VE BEEN DESIGNING...
NONSTOP.

626
00:57:44.390 --> 00:57:47.400
THAT'S WONDERFUL.
GLAD TO HEAR
YOU'VE BEEN PRODUCTIVE.

627
00:57:51.900 --> 00:57:54.900
TO BE PERFECTLY FRANK.

628
00:57:54.900 --> 00:57:57.410
I WAS A LITTLE SURPRISED
TO HEAR FROM YOU.

629
00:58:00.410 --> 00:58:04.410
- IS THERE SOMETHING WRONG ?
- NO.  WHY ?

630
00:58:04.410 --> 00:58:07.420
WELL.
IT'S USUALLY THE CASE...

631
00:58:07.420 --> 00:58:09.920
WHEN YOU GET A CALL
FROM SOMEONE YOU HAVEN'T
HEARD FROM FOR A WHILE.

632
00:58:09.920 --> 00:58:13.420
EVERYTHING'S FINE.

633
00:58:16.430 --> 00:58:18.440
<i>ACTUALLY.</i>

634
00:58:21.930 --> 00:58:24.430
I HAVE A FAVOR TO ASK.

635
00:58:28.440 --> 00:58:29.940
<i>[ Screaming ]</i>

636
00:58:29.940 --> 00:58:33.440
YOU SMUG FUCK !

637
00:58:33.440 --> 00:58:35.940
WHAT IS IT ?

638
00:58:40.450 --> 00:58:41.950
I NEED TO BORROW MONEY.

639
00:58:42.450 --> 00:58:44.450
MAY I ASK WHAT FOR ?

640
00:58:46.460 --> 00:58:50.970
COULD YOU TURN
            THE LIGHT OFF ?
WHY DO YOU WANT THE LIGHT OFF ?

641
00:58:50.960 --> 00:58:53.460
I JUST DO.

642
00:58:53.460 --> 00:58:56.460
YOU NEVER DID BEFORE.
            PLEASE. ARNOLD.

643
00:59:22.490 --> 00:59:25.990
<i>[ TV Indistinct ]</i>

644
01:00:17.000 --> 01:00:19.500
[ Door Closes ]

645
01:00:33.510 --> 01:00:36.010
<i>[ Elevator Bell Rings ]</i>

646
01:02:25.120 --> 01:02:29.130
WHERE IS EVERYBODY ?
            I DON'T KNOW. MAN.

647
01:02:29.130 --> 01:02:32.130
ALL ANGEL SAID WAS
MEET AT WALDBAUM'S.

648
01:02:34.630 --> 01:02:38.640
YOU SURE THIS IS
THE RIGHT WALDBAUM'S ?
            YEAH. I'M POSITIVE.

649
01:02:39.640 --> 01:02:43.640
YOU JUST WATCH MY BACK.
AND I'LL WATCH YOURS.

650
01:02:47.150 --> 01:02:51.150
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE WE SUPPOSED TO DO NOW ?
                    HEY.

651
01:03:02.660 --> 01:03:04.660
EVERYONE AND THEIR MOTHER.

652
01:03:06.170 --> 01:03:08.680
YEAH. THE TRUCK'S GONNA BE HERE.
BACK UP.

653
01:03:11.170 --> 01:03:12.670
BACK UP.

654
01:03:19.180 --> 01:03:21.180
[ Cheering ]

655
01:03:27.190 --> 01:03:29.690
[ Cheering ]

656
01:04:11.730 --> 01:04:15.230
[ Excited Chattering ]

657
01:04:16.240 --> 01:04:20.250
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

658
01:04:32.750 --> 01:04:35.750
<i>[ Horn Honking ]</i>

659
01:04:35.760 --> 01:04:37.770
COME BACK !

660
01:04:40.760 --> 01:04:42.760
STUPID FUCKIN' JUNKIE !
WE'RE FUCKED !

661
01:04:42.760 --> 01:04:45.260
-MOTHERFUCKER'S GOIN'
 BACK TO FLORIDA.
-IT WAS THE LAST SHIP FOR MILES.

662
01:04:45.260 --> 01:04:47.270
SITTIN' THEIR ASSES
IN THE SUN...

663
01:04:47.270 --> 01:04:51.770
<i>WHILE WE SIT HERE ASS DEEP
IN SOME MOTHERFUCKIN' SNOW.</i>

664
01:04:51.770 --> 01:04:56.270
HEY. WHAT WOULD HAPPEN
IF WE WENT DOWN THERE TO COP ?

665
01:04:56.280 --> 01:04:59.290
- ARE YOU SERIOUS ?
- WHY NOT ?

666
01:04:59.280 --> 01:05:03.280
WHAT THE FUCK ARE YOU SAYIN' ?
WE SUPPOSED TO WALK UP TO
SOME ROOM CLERK AT SOME HOTEL...

667
01:05:03.780 --> 01:05:05.780
AND ASK HIM
        FOR A CONNECTION ?
<i>GET WITH IT !</i>

668
01:05:05.790 --> 01:05:09.800
YOU TELLING ME
YOU CAN'T NOSE OUT SOME DOPE
WHEN IT'S AROUND ?

669
01:05:09.790 --> 01:05:12.790
MAN. WE GOT NOTHIN'
TO LOSE.

670
01:05:12.790 --> 01:05:15.790
<i>IT'S WIDE OPEN.
AND IF WE GET THERE
RIGHT AWAY.</i>

671
01:05:15.800 --> 01:05:20.310
WE CAN NAME OUR OWN PRICE. AND
WE CAN SIT BACK AND HAVE THOSE
FOOLS COVER THE STREET FOR US.

672
01:05:22.300 --> 01:05:27.310
YEAH. MAN.  LAST SUMMER
WAS A MOTHERFUCKIN' BALL.
HUH. JIM ?

673
01:05:31.310 --> 01:05:35.310
IT SEEMS LIKE
A THOUSAND YEARS AGO
SINCE LAST SUMMER. MAN.

674
01:05:35.310 --> 01:05:37.320
IT'LL BE LIKE THAT
AGAIN. MAN.

675
01:05:41.820 --> 01:05:44.320
I COULD GET ANGEL
TO GET US A SHORT...

676
01:05:44.320 --> 01:05:46.820
IF WE PROMISE HIM
SOME DYNAMITE SCAG.

677
01:05:46.830 --> 01:05:48.840
[ Chuckles ]

678
01:06:05.850 --> 01:06:07.860
<i>[ Phone Beeping ]</i>

679
01:06:10.350 --> 01:06:13.350
<i>[ Beeping Continues ]</i>

680
01:06:46.890 --> 01:06:49.400
<i>[ Beeping Continues ]</i>

681
01:07:04.400 --> 01:07:07.410
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN ?

682
01:07:07.410 --> 01:07:10.410
WHERE THE HELL
YOU THINK I'VE BEEN ?

683
01:07:10.410 --> 01:07:13.410
- WHERE'S THE SCORE ?
- WELL. WE HAD A BIT
  OF A PROBLEM.

684
01:07:13.410 --> 01:07:17.420
I MEAN.
EVERYTHING WAS GOIN' GOOD.
AND THEN...

685
01:07:17.420 --> 01:07:19.880
<i>SOME DUMB ASS JUNKIE--
   </i>DID WHAT ?

686
01:07:20.390 --> 01:07:21.900
<i>SOME DUMB ASS JUNKIE
DID WHAT ?</i>

687
01:07:22.390 --> 01:07:25.390
- YOU MEAN YOU FUCKED IT UP ?
- WHAT THE FUCK
  IS WRONG WITH YOU ?

688
01:07:25.390 --> 01:07:27.890
YOU PROMISED ME
EVERYTHING WAS GONNA BE OKAY.

689
01:07:27.890 --> 01:07:31.900
<i>I FUCKED THAT SLEEZEBAG FOR YOU.
I PUT MYSELF THROUGH
FUCKING HELL FOR YOU !</i>

690
01:07:31.900 --> 01:07:34.400
- THERE'S NOTHING OUT THERE !
- I DON'T GIVE A SHIT !

691
01:07:34.400 --> 01:07:37.900
<i>YOU FUCKING LOSER !</i>

692
01:07:39.410 --> 01:07:41.920
YOU WANNA BE SURE
WE HAVE SOME EXTRA STUFF ?

693
01:07:41.910 --> 01:07:44.910
<i>TY TOLD ME ABOUT A GUY
WHO'S HOLDING SOME WEIGHT.</i>

694
01:07:44.910 --> 01:07:47.910
<i>BUT HE AIN'T
SELLIN' IT !</i>

695
01:07:47.910 --> 01:07:50.920
<i>- [ Ty ]  YEAH ?
</i>- TY. GIMME THAT GUY'S NUMBER.

696
01:07:50.920 --> 01:07:52.920
WHAT GUY ?
THE GUY WHO LIKES BROADS !

697
01:07:52.920 --> 01:07:56.420
<i>[ Ty ]  WHY ?
JUST GIMME
THE FUCKIN' NUMBER !</i>

698
01:07:56.420 --> 01:08:00.420
934-8777.

699
01:08:01.930 --> 01:08:05.930
<i>YOU WORRIED SO MUCH.
GO FIX YOURSELF WITH HIM !</i>

700
01:08:05.930 --> 01:08:10.430
YOU WON'T HAVE TO FUCKIN'
WAIT AROUND SO MUCH. AND I WON'T
FREEZE MY ASS IN THE STREET !

701
01:08:10.440 --> 01:08:12.450
<i>[ Door Slams Shut ]</i>

702
01:08:46.470 --> 01:08:48.970
<i>- [ Audience Applauding ]
</i>- ALL RIGHT. WE GOT A WINNER.

703
01:08:48.970 --> 01:08:50.980
<i>[ Audience ]
WE GOT A WINNER.
WE GOT A WINNER.</i>

704
01:08:50.980 --> 01:08:54.480
- WE GOT A WINNER.
- WE GOT A WINNER.

705
01:08:54.480 --> 01:08:58.480
<i>SHE'S A BEAUTIFUL WOMAN
WITH A WINNING SENSE OF HUMOR
AND A MAGICAL SMILE.</i>

706
01:08:58.480 --> 01:09:02.490
SHE'S REALLY GONNA WIN
YOUR HEART.  STRAIGHT FROM
BRIGHTON BEACH. BROOKLYN.

707
01:09:02.490 --> 01:09:07.990
PLEASE GIVE A JUICY WELCOME
TO OUR VERY OWN
MRS. SARA GOLDFARB !

708
01:09:07.990 --> 01:09:10.490
<i>[ Audience ]
JUICE BY SARA !
JUICE BY SARA !</i>

709
01:09:10.500 --> 01:09:13.010
<i>OOOH. SARA !</i>

710
01:09:14.000 --> 01:09:18.000
<i>OOOH. SARA !
[ Cheering. Applause ]</i>

711
01:09:18.000 --> 01:09:21.010
<i>[ Red Sara ]
IT'S A PLEASURE TO BE HERE.
IT'S A PLEASURE TO HAVE YOU.</i>

712
01:09:21.010 --> 01:09:24.010
<i>AND THAT IS ONE
SMASHING DRESS YOU HAVE ON.</i>

713
01:09:24.010 --> 01:09:26.510
<i>[ Cheering. Applause ]</i>

714
01:09:27.010 --> 01:09:29.010
THANK YOU.
TAPPY. IF YOU DON'T MIND.

715
01:09:29.520 --> 01:09:32.530
<i>I WOULD LIKE TO SAY HELLO
TO MY HUSBAND SEYMOUR.</i>

716
01:09:32.520 --> 01:09:35.520
<i>AND TO MY BEAUTIFUL.
SUCCESSFUL SON HAROLD.</i>

717
01:09:37.520 --> 01:09:40.520
<i>I HOPE YOU'RE IN LOVE.</i>

718
01:09:40.530 --> 01:09:44.540
<i>PLEASE COME AND SEE ME.
AND BRING MARION. WON'T YOU ?</i>

719
01:09:44.530 --> 01:09:47.530
I'M SURE HE'LL BE HERE SOON.

720
01:09:47.530 --> 01:09:50.030
IT'S ALMOST THAT TIME.
ARE YOU READY ?

721
01:09:50.040 --> 01:09:52.050
I'M READY. TAPPY.

722
01:09:52.040 --> 01:09:54.540
<i>[ Audience Gasps ]</i>

723
01:09:54.540 --> 01:09:57.040
NOT TO WORRY.
 NOT TO WORRY.

724
01:10:00.050 --> 01:10:02.560
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE ?

725
01:10:02.550 --> 01:10:05.550
WHY ARE YOU HERE ?

726
01:10:05.550 --> 01:10:08.550
- WHAT DO YOU WANT ?
- OH. TAPPY !

727
01:10:09.050 --> 01:10:11.560
<i>JOIN US IN CREATING
EXCELLENCE.</i>

728
01:10:11.560 --> 01:10:14.560
OH. I THOUGHT
YOU'D NEVER ASK.

729
01:10:14.560 --> 01:10:17.060
<i>[ Audience Gasps ]</i>

730
01:10:18.560 --> 01:10:21.070
LOOK AT THIS.

731
01:10:21.070 --> 01:10:24.570
- IT'S DISGUSTING.
- WHAT DO YOU EXPECT ?

732
01:10:24.570 --> 01:10:27.570
- [ Laughing ]
- COULD YOU DO ANY BETTER ?

733
01:10:29.580 --> 01:10:33.590
IT'S AN OLD BUILDING.
IT HASN'T BEEN PAINTED
IN YEARS.

734
01:10:33.580 --> 01:10:36.580
I'M OLD !  ALONE !

735
01:10:36.580 --> 01:10:38.580
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

736
01:10:38.580 --> 01:10:41.090
PLEASE.  I'LL EXPLAIN.

737
01:10:44.090 --> 01:10:46.090
[ Laughing ]

738
01:10:46.090 --> 01:10:48.590
<i>[ Laughing ]</i>

739
01:11:10.620 --> 01:11:12.630
[ Gasps ]

740
01:11:22.630 --> 01:11:25.630
WHAT IS THAT ?
I DON'T WANT THAT !

741
01:11:25.630 --> 01:11:28.130
WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?
GET AWAY FROM ME !

742
01:11:28.130 --> 01:11:30.130
- READY. MRS. GOLDFARB.
- READY FOR WHAT ?

743
01:11:30.140 --> 01:11:32.150
THREE. TWO. ONE.

744
01:11:32.140 --> 01:11:36.140
<i>♪ [ Game Show Music ]</i>

745
01:11:36.140 --> 01:11:43.650
♪

746
01:12:23.690 --> 01:12:27.190
FEED ME. SARA.
 FEED ME. SARA.

747
01:12:27.190 --> 01:12:30.190
- [ Together ]
  FEED ME. SARA.
- FEED ME. SARA.

748
01:12:30.200 --> 01:12:34.210
<i>[ Chanting ]
FEED ME. SARA !  FEED ME. SARA !</i>

749
01:12:34.700 --> 01:12:38.200
[ Chanting Continues ]

750
01:12:38.200 --> 01:12:43.210
FEED ME. SARA !
 FEED ME. SARA !

751
01:12:44.710 --> 01:12:48.710
JESUS !
TELL THEM TO STOP !
PLEASE !

752
01:12:48.710 --> 01:12:51.720
[ Screaming ]

753
01:13:24.750 --> 01:13:27.750
<i>[ Harry ]
THANK YOU. ANGEL.</i>

754
01:13:28.250 --> 01:13:33.760
WHOO-HOO !  SURE HOPE
THIS MOTHERFUCKER WORKS.
MY ASS COULD USE SOME HEAT.

755
01:13:33.760 --> 01:13:37.760
<i>HOW LONG YOU THINK
THIS TRIP'S GONNA TAKE ?
    </i>WE'LL MAKE IT IN A DAY.

756
01:13:37.760 --> 01:13:41.770
A DAY ?  SHIT !
CALIFORNIA.

757
01:13:41.770 --> 01:13:45.270
<i>HERE WE COME.
IT'S FLORIDA. TY.
FLORIDA.</i>

758
01:13:45.270 --> 01:13:50.270
CALIFORNIA. FLORIDA--
EITHER WAY. YOUR PALE ASS
GETTING A TAN. RIGHT ?

759
01:13:53.780 --> 01:13:56.280
<i>[ Sara ]
DO YOU KNOW IF THIS TRAIN
GOES TO MADISON AVENUE ?</i>

760
01:13:56.280 --> 01:13:59.780
DO YOU KNOW MAYLIN AND BLOCK ?
I HAVE THEIR ADDRESS.

761
01:13:59.790 --> 01:14:04.300
IT'S ON MADISON AVENUE.
I'M GONNA BE ON TELEVISION.

762
01:14:04.290 --> 01:14:05.790
YOU'RE WHACKED !

763
01:14:07.290 --> 01:14:10.290
HEY !  HEY !  HELLO ?

764
01:14:10.800 --> 01:14:12.810
DO YOU KNOW IF THIS TRAIN
GOES TO MADISON AVENUE ?

765
01:14:14.800 --> 01:14:16.800
I'M GONNA BE ON TELEVISION !

766
01:14:18.300 --> 01:14:22.810
I JUST HAVE TO FIND OUT WHEN.

767
01:14:22.810 --> 01:14:25.310
FLORIDA.

768
01:14:27.810 --> 01:14:31.820
WHEN IS HE GONNA BE BACK ?

769
01:14:31.820 --> 01:14:36.820
A FEW DAYS ?
ANGEL. WHAT AM I SUPPOSED
TO DO ?

770
01:14:36.820 --> 01:14:39.820
PLEASE. YOU GOTTA HELP ME.

771
01:14:39.830 --> 01:14:43.840
COME ON.
I CAN GET YOU MONEY.

772
01:14:43.830 --> 01:14:46.830
ANGEL.
THERE'S GOTTA BE SOMETHING.
ANYTHING.  HELP ME.

773
01:14:46.830 --> 01:14:49.830
<i>WHY AREN'T YOU CALLING ME ?</i>

774
01:14:50.340 --> 01:14:53.350
I HAVE TO KNOW WHEN
I'M GONNA BE ON TELEVISION.

775
01:14:54.840 --> 01:14:57.340
I'M SARA GOLDFARB.

776
01:14:57.340 --> 01:15:02.350
AND YOU SHOULD TELL ME
WHEN I'M GONNA BE ON TELEVISION.

777
01:15:02.350 --> 01:15:04.350
<i>JUST SIT FOR A MOMENT.
I'LL RING THEM.</i>

778
01:15:04.350 --> 01:15:06.350
I JUST WANNA KNOW WHEN.

779
01:15:06.850 --> 01:15:11.860
MAYBE YOU LOST MY CARD !
PLEASE. DARLING. HAVE A LOOK.
AND YOU'LL TELL ME.

780
01:15:13.360 --> 01:15:15.860
IT'S NOT THE PRIZES.
I'LL GIVE THEM AWAY.

781
01:15:16.860 --> 01:15:19.360
I JUST WANNA BE
ON THE SHOW.

782
01:15:19.360 --> 01:15:21.870
I'VE WAITED SO LONG...

783
01:15:21.870 --> 01:15:27.370
TO BE ON WITH MY HARRY
AND MY GRANDSON.

784
01:15:27.370 --> 01:15:29.870
MRS. GOLDFARB.
SIP THIS.

785
01:15:29.880 --> 01:15:33.390
<i>SOMETIMES IT TAKES A WHILE
TO GET CALLED FOR A SHOW.
MRS. GOLDFARB.</i>

786
01:15:33.380 --> 01:15:36.880
OH.  OOOH.
<i>[ Door Closes ]</i>

787
01:15:39.380 --> 01:15:40.880
- THIS HER ?
- <i>YES.</i>

788
01:15:41.390 --> 01:15:45.390
- CAN YOU WALK ?
- I'M WALKIN'
  ACROSS THE STAGE !

789
01:15:45.390 --> 01:15:49.390
AND YOU SHOULD SEE MY HARRY
ON TELEVISION.

790
01:15:49.390 --> 01:15:51.900
WE'RE GIVING THE PRIZES AWAY.

791
01:15:51.900 --> 01:15:55.400
I JUST WANTED TO BE
ON THE SHOW !

792
01:15:55.400 --> 01:15:57.400
[ Sobbing ]

793
01:15:57.400 --> 01:15:59.900
<i>[ Paramedic ]  WHAT'S HER NAME ?
WE THINK IT'S
SARA GOLDFARB.</i>

794
01:16:00.410 --> 01:16:04.920
<i>CALL SEYMOUR AND TELL HIM
TO MEET ME AT THE BEAUTY PARLOR.</i>

795
01:16:04.910 --> 01:16:07.410
I'VE GOT THE RED DRESS THAT
I WORE TO HARRY'S GRADUATION.

796
01:16:07.910 --> 01:16:09.910
AND THE GOLD SHOES.
<i>OKAY. MRS. GOLDFARB.</i>

797
01:16:09.920 --> 01:16:12.430
HERE WE GO.

798
01:16:12.420 --> 01:16:14.420
ONE. TWO. THREE--

799
01:16:14.420 --> 01:16:17.920
LET'S TAKE IT
NICE AND EASY.

800
01:16:27.930 --> 01:16:29.930
<i>[ Dial Tone ]</i>

801
01:16:29.940 --> 01:16:33.950
<i>[ Numbers Dialing ]</i>

802
01:16:36.940 --> 01:16:38.940
[ Ringing ]

803
01:16:40.950 --> 01:16:43.460
[ Big Tim ]
YEAH ?
[ Disconnects ]

804
01:16:53.410 --> 01:16:56.410
<i>[ Numbers Dialing ]</i>

805
01:17:03.420 --> 01:17:05.420
[ Ringing ]

806
01:17:05.420 --> 01:17:07.420
[ Big Tim ]
YEAH ?

807
01:17:09.420 --> 01:17:11.930
[ Whispering ]
        HI.
[ Chuckling ]

808
01:17:13.930 --> 01:17:18.930
TELL ROSE I'M GOING TO BE
ON TELEVISION.

809
01:17:22.440 --> 01:17:25.440
<i>[ Siren Wailing ]</i>

810
01:17:33.450 --> 01:17:37.450
[ Sighs ]
WHOO.

811
01:17:46.460 --> 01:17:48.960
OH. SHIT !

812
01:17:48.960 --> 01:17:50.960
GODDAMN !
HOW LONG YOU HAD THAT ?

813
01:17:50.970 --> 01:17:53.480
JUST A FEW DAYS.

814
01:17:53.970 --> 01:17:57.970
- THAT SHIT DON'T LOOK TOO GOOD.
- IT DON'T FEEL TOO GOOD
  EITHER. MAN.

815
01:18:00.480 --> 01:18:02.990
BUT A LITTLE STUFF
WILL TAKE CARE OF THAT.

816
01:18:02.980 --> 01:18:04.980
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU ?
DON'T SHOOT IN THERE !

817
01:18:04.980 --> 01:18:07.980
I'LL BLOW IT IF I DON'T.

818
01:18:07.980 --> 01:18:09.980
FUCK IT.

819
01:18:20.500 --> 01:18:24.010
OH.  SHIT.

820
01:18:34.010 --> 01:18:36.510
<i>[ Buzzer Buzzing ]</i>

821
01:18:38.510 --> 01:18:42.520
- HI. HOW ARE YOU ?
  CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
- YES. SEYMOUR.

822
01:18:42.520 --> 01:18:46.020
- TAKE ANYTHING ?
- I TOOK MY RED DRESS AND--

823
01:18:46.020 --> 01:18:49.020
- NO EMERGENCY.
  TAKE HER TO PSYCH.
- TELEVISION.

824
01:18:58.030 --> 01:19:00.530
COME ON IN.

825
01:19:04.540 --> 01:19:06.540
THANKS.

826
01:19:11.050 --> 01:19:14.560
WHAT'S YOUR NAME ?

827
01:19:14.550 --> 01:19:16.550
MARION.

828
01:19:16.550 --> 01:19:18.550
<i>WELL.
WHAT DO YOU KNOW ?</i>

829
01:19:18.550 --> 01:19:21.050
MAID MARION.

830
01:19:21.060 --> 01:19:25.570
<i>[ Laughing ]</i>

831
01:19:26.560 --> 01:19:28.560
I'M LITTLE JOHN.

832
01:19:32.070 --> 01:19:35.570
- YOU HAVE A BEAUTIFUL VIEW.
- YOU KNOW WHAT I LIKE BEST
  ABOUT PATTY CHICKS ?

833
01:19:37.570 --> 01:19:41.070
THEY GIVE GOOD HEAD.

834
01:19:41.080 --> 01:19:43.090
BLACK BROADS
DON'T KNOW NOTHIN'
ABOUT NO HEAD.

835
01:19:43.080 --> 01:19:45.080
I DON'T KNOW WHY.

836
01:19:45.080 --> 01:19:48.580
MAYBE IT HAS SOMETHING TO DO
WITH SOME ANCIENT TRIBAL CUSTOM.

837
01:19:48.580 --> 01:19:51.590
[ Chuckling ]

838
01:19:53.090 --> 01:19:55.090
COME HERE.

839
01:20:06.600 --> 01:20:10.100
MMM.  MMM.

840
01:20:10.110 --> 01:20:12.620
BETTER SAVE
SOME OF THAT ENERGY.

841
01:20:15.610 --> 01:20:18.610
COME HERE.

842
01:20:29.120 --> 01:20:31.630
I KNOW IT'S PRETTY.
BABY.

843
01:20:31.630 --> 01:20:33.630
BUT I DIDN'T TAKE IT OUT
FOR AIR.

844
01:20:50.650 --> 01:20:53.660
I TOLD YOUR ASS
STAY AWAY FROM THAT ARM.

845
01:20:53.650 --> 01:20:56.150
<i>SEE ?</i>

846
01:20:56.150 --> 01:20:58.150
I GOTTA CALL MARION.
MAN.

847
01:20:58.150 --> 01:21:01.660
THAT'S ABOUT TO BE
A LONG DISTANCE CALL NOW.

848
01:21:01.660 --> 01:21:06.160
<i>THAT'S 600 MILES !
WE ARE 600 MILES CLOSER
TO MIAMI.</i>

849
01:21:06.660 --> 01:21:10.660
IT'S ALSO 600 MILES
FURTHER AWAY FROM NEW YORK.

850
01:21:15.170 --> 01:21:19.670
<i>I KNOW WHERE YOU CAN PICK UP
A REAL NICE TASTE.
THOUGH IT'S MORE LIKE PLAY.</i>

851
01:21:19.670 --> 01:21:22.180
SUNDAY NIGHT WE'RE THROWING
A LITTLE GATHERING.

852
01:21:22.180 --> 01:21:24.680
ALL GOOD PEOPLE.

853
01:21:24.680 --> 01:21:27.180
I CAN'T. I'M BUSY.

854
01:21:27.180 --> 01:21:29.180
ANYWAY.
I'M NOT REALLY HOOKED.

855
01:21:29.180 --> 01:21:32.190
OH. I KNOW.
BUT IT'S A REAL NICE TASTE.

856
01:21:38.690 --> 01:21:41.190
I'LL SEE YOU SUNDAY.
MAID MARION.

857
01:21:42.700 --> 01:21:45.200
OKAY. MRS. GOLDFARB. JUST TRY
AND ANSWER MY QUESTIONS.
OKAY ?

858
01:21:45.200 --> 01:21:50.200
- WHEN DID YOU START TAKING
  THE PILLS ?
- OH. THE SUMMER.

859
01:21:50.210 --> 01:21:55.720
- YOU STARTED LAST SUMMER ?
- I GOT THE BEST PLACE
  IN THE SUN.

860
01:21:55.710 --> 01:21:58.210
ADA FIXED MY HAIR.
<i>EVERYTHING IS GONNA BE
ALL RIGHT.</i>

861
01:21:58.210 --> 01:22:01.210
WE'LL GET YOU FIXED UP
IN NO TIME.

862
01:22:19.230 --> 01:22:22.240
[ Screaming ]

863
01:22:22.240 --> 01:22:27.740
- HOLD TIGHT. MAN.
- I CAN'T CUT IT.  I GOTTA DO
  SOMETHING ABOUT THIS ARM.

864
01:22:27.740 --> 01:22:31.240
LET ME SEE WHAT
IT LOOKS LIKE.

865
01:22:36.250 --> 01:22:39.250
OH. DAMN. JIM !

866
01:22:39.250 --> 01:22:41.760
OH. MAN.

867
01:22:41.760 --> 01:22:44.260
THAT'S THE UGLIEST MOTHERFUCKER
I'VE EVER SEEN.

868
01:22:44.260 --> 01:22:49.760
- I GOTTA CALL MARION.
- FUCK THAT.  WE GOTTA GET YOU
  TO A HOSPITAL. MAN.

869
01:22:54.270 --> 01:22:56.770
WHAT IS THAT ?

870
01:22:56.770 --> 01:23:00.270
<i>I DON'T WANT THAT.
 I DON'T WANT THAT !</i>

871
01:23:00.280 --> 01:23:02.790
[ Moaning ]

872
01:23:15.790 --> 01:23:18.290
[ Groaning ]
<i>[ Phone Ringing ]</i>

873
01:23:38.810 --> 01:23:40.810
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM ?

874
01:23:40.820 --> 01:23:43.830
IT'S MY ARM.
MY ARM IS KILLIN' ME.

875
01:23:43.820 --> 01:23:46.320
LET'S HAVE A LOOK AT IT.

876
01:23:46.320 --> 01:23:50.820
- [ Groaning ]
- ALL RIGHT.

877
01:23:54.830 --> 01:23:57.330
I'LL BE BACK
IN A MINUTE.

878
01:24:22.860 --> 01:24:25.860
I WANNA PLAY BLACKJACK
ALL NIGHT LONG.

879
01:24:25.860 --> 01:24:28.860
<i>SO I MAKE UP THIS ROUTINE.
I TELL THEM. "YOU GO AHEAD.
I DON'T FEEL GOOD.</i>

880
01:24:28.860 --> 01:24:32.870
YOU GO HAVE A GOOD TIME
DANCING."  SURE ENOUGH.
THEY LEAVE THE ROOM.

881
01:24:32.870 --> 01:24:35.370
READY ?
ONE. TWO AND THREE.

882
01:24:37.870 --> 01:24:42.880
<i>AS SOON AS THEY LEAVE.
I GO RUNNING BACK TO THE CASINO.
SIT AT MY BLACKJACK TABLE.</i>

883
01:24:42.880 --> 01:24:44.880
<i>I AM THERE
FOR THE WHOLE NIGHT.</i>

884
01:24:45.380 --> 01:24:50.880
<i>FINALLY. I GET UP SO BIG.
I GOT $500 BLACK CHIPS
IN MY POCKET.</i>

885
01:24:50.890 --> 01:24:53.400
<i>I SWEAR TO GOD.
THE HOURS ARE GOING BY.</i>

886
01:24:53.390 --> 01:24:57.390
<i>I'M LAYING BACK.
I'M HITTIN' ON HARD SEVENTEENS.
IT WAS BEAUTIFUL.</i>

887
01:24:57.390 --> 01:25:00.390
[ Groaning ]
NEXT THING I KNOW. THIS GUY
IS SITTING NEXT TO ME.

888
01:25:00.900 --> 01:25:05.410
<i>HE'S A SECURITY GUARD.
TELLING ME I HAVE TO LEAVE.</i>

889
01:25:05.400 --> 01:25:07.900
<i>I'M LIKE.
"WHY YOU TELLING ME
 I HAVE TO LEAVE ?"</i>

890
01:25:07.900 --> 01:25:11.910
HE SAYS. "YOU HAVE
TO LEAVE BECAUSE--"

891
01:25:11.910 --> 01:25:16.410
<i>[ Attendant Continues
  Indistinct ]</i>

892
01:25:16.410 --> 01:25:17.910
SWALLOW.

893
01:25:21.420 --> 01:25:24.430
SWALLOW.

894
01:25:36.930 --> 01:25:42.440
<i>[ Footsteps
  Approaching ]</i>

895
01:25:53.950 --> 01:25:57.450
YOU HAVE TO EAT. MRS. GOLDFARB.
IF WE'RE GONNA GET YOU HEALTHY.
YOU HAVE TO EAT.

896
01:25:57.450 --> 01:25:59.950
WORK WITH
THE ATTENDANTS.

897
01:25:59.950 --> 01:26:02.460
I'M GONNA TRY
SOME NEW MEDICATIONS.

898
01:26:08.460 --> 01:26:10.960
[ Groaning ]

899
01:26:23.480 --> 01:26:28.980
[ Groaning ]

900
01:26:36.990 --> 01:26:39.990
<i>[ Muffled Screams ]</i>

901
01:26:48.500 --> 01:26:50.500
<i>[ Phone Ringing ]</i>

902
01:26:54.010 --> 01:26:57.510
[ Ringing Continues ]

903
01:27:04.520 --> 01:27:07.020
HELLO.
    [ Harry ]
    MARION.

904
01:27:08.520 --> 01:27:11.020
HARRY ?

905
01:27:11.030 --> 01:27:16.040
MARION. I'VE BEEN
THINKING ABOUT YOU SO MUCH.

906
01:27:16.030 --> 01:27:18.030
ARE YOU OKAY ?

907
01:27:20.030 --> 01:27:24.040
- WHEN YOU COMIN' HOME ?
- SOON.

908
01:27:24.040 --> 01:27:28.540
- WHEN ?
- SOON.

909
01:27:28.540 --> 01:27:31.540
YOU HOLDIN' OUT
ALL RIGHT ?

910
01:27:31.550 --> 01:27:33.560
HARRY ?

911
01:27:36.050 --> 01:27:38.050
CAN YOU COME TODAY ?

912
01:27:41.060 --> 01:27:45.570
[ Sighs ]
YEAH.

913
01:27:45.560 --> 01:27:48.060
[ Crying ]

914
01:27:50.060 --> 01:27:52.070
I'LL COME.

915
01:27:52.070 --> 01:27:56.070
[ Crying ]
I'LL COME TODAY.

916
01:28:00.070 --> 01:28:03.580
JUST WAIT FOR ME.
ALL RIGHT ?

917
01:28:06.580 --> 01:28:10.580
OKAY. HARRY.
I'M COMING BACK.
MARION.

918
01:28:10.590 --> 01:28:13.600
YEAH.
             YEAH.
MARION ?

919
01:28:15.090 --> 01:28:17.090
I'M SORRY. MARION.

920
01:28:17.090 --> 01:28:19.090
I KNOW.

921
01:28:28.100 --> 01:28:30.100
<i>[ Doctor ]
MRS. GOLDFARB ?</i>

922
01:28:32.610 --> 01:28:35.610
YOU ALL RIGHT ?

923
01:28:35.610 --> 01:28:41.110
<i>UM. SO. MRS. GOLDFARB.
WE'VE TRIED
SEVERAL MEDICATIONS.</i>

924
01:28:41.120 --> 01:28:43.630
<i>AND YOU DON'T SEEM
TO BE RESPONDING.</i>

925
01:28:44.120 --> 01:28:48.120
<i>WE MIGHT BE AT A POINT
WHERE WE MIGHT WANT TO TRY
SOME ALTERNATIVE METHODS.</i>

926
01:28:48.120 --> 01:28:53.130
<i>WE'VE HAD EXCELLENT RESULTS
WITH E.C.T. IN THE PAST.</i>

927
01:28:53.130 --> 01:28:57.130
<i>SO IF I CAN JUST GET
YOUR JOHN HANCOCK.</i>

928
01:28:57.130 --> 01:28:59.630
WE'LL GET UNDERWAY.

929
01:28:59.630 --> 01:29:01.630
<i>GREAT.  THANKS.</i>

930
01:29:01.640 --> 01:29:04.150
[ Groaning ]
OH. JESUS CHRIST !

931
01:29:04.640 --> 01:29:08.140
<i>SOMEBODY HELP US.
        </i>I NEED A DOCTOR. MAN.

932
01:29:08.640 --> 01:29:11.640
MY FRIEND IS SICK.
GIVE HIM SOME HELP. PLEASE.

933
01:29:11.650 --> 01:29:16.660
I CAN'T TAKE IT. MAN !
MY ARM !  MY FUCKIN' ARM !

934
01:29:16.650 --> 01:29:18.650
HELP ME !

935
01:29:18.650 --> 01:29:23.160
HELP US !  SOMEBODY
FUCKIN' HELP US. PLEASE !

936
01:29:34.170 --> 01:29:36.170
[ Knocks ]

937
01:29:38.670 --> 01:29:40.670
<i>[ Door Opens ]</i>

938
01:29:43.680 --> 01:29:46.680
MAID MARION.  WELCOME.
[ Chuckling ]

939
01:29:46.680 --> 01:29:48.680
CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
 CAN YOU SEE ME ?

940
01:29:48.680 --> 01:29:50.680
YES. SIR.
OKAY FOR WORK.

941
01:29:50.690 --> 01:29:52.700
<i>CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
 CAN YOU SEE ME ?</i>

942
01:29:52.690 --> 01:29:55.190
<i>[ Inmate ]
YES. SIR.
OKAY FOR WORK.</i>

943
01:29:55.690 --> 01:29:56.690
<i>CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
 CAN YOU SEE ME ?</i>

944
01:29:57.190 --> 01:29:58.690
<i>[ Inmate ]
YES. SIR.
OKAY FOR WORK.</i>

945
01:29:59.190 --> 01:30:01.190
<i>CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
 CAN YOU SEE ME ?</i>

946
01:30:01.200 --> 01:30:03.710
<i>[ Inmate ]
YES. SIR.
OKAY FOR WORK.</i>

947
01:30:04.200 --> 01:30:07.700
<i>CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
 CAN YOU SEE ME ?
YES. SIR.</i>

948
01:30:07.700 --> 01:30:09.200
<i>[ Big Tim ]
FELLAS. MEET MARION.</i>

949
01:30:09.700 --> 01:30:11.700
<i>[ Men Cheering ]</i>

950
01:30:11.710 --> 01:30:14.720
<i>CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
 CAN YOU SEE ME ?</i>

951
01:30:14.710 --> 01:30:16.710
<i>[ Inmate ]
YES. SIR.
OKAY FOR WORK.</i>

952
01:30:17.210 --> 01:30:18.710
<i>CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
 CAN YOU SEE ME ?</i>

953
01:30:19.210 --> 01:30:20.710
<i>[ Inmate ]
YES. SIR.
OKAY FOR WORK.</i>

954
01:30:20.720 --> 01:30:23.730
- [ Cheering ]
- SHOW TIME.

955
01:30:23.720 --> 01:30:27.220
<i>OKAY FOR WORK.
CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
CAN YOU SEE ME ?</i>

956
01:30:27.220 --> 01:30:30.220
- YES.
- SAY. "SIR."

957
01:30:30.220 --> 01:30:33.730
<i>GODDAMN NEW YORK
DOPE FIEND NIGGERS.
LEARN SOME MANNERS.</i>

958
01:30:33.730 --> 01:30:36.230
CAN YOU HEAR ME ?
 CAN YOU SEE ME ?

959
01:30:36.230 --> 01:30:40.230
- YES. SIR.
- <i>OKAY FOR WORK.</i>

960
01:30:40.230 --> 01:30:42.740
GOT A MOUTHPIECE.
<i>CAN YOU HEAR ME ?</i>

961
01:30:42.740 --> 01:30:45.740
- <i>CAN YOU SEE ME ?
</i>- SAYS HE'S GOT SOMETHING WRONG
  WITH HIS ARM.

962
01:30:45.740 --> 01:30:47.740
[ Screams ]

963
01:30:47.740 --> 01:30:51.740
<i>- I DON'T THINK HE'LL BE PUTTIN'
  ANY MORE DOPE IN THAT ARM.
</i>- SMELLS WORSE THAN HE DO.

964
01:30:51.750 --> 01:30:56.260
<i>[ Prison Doctor ]  GET HIM OVER
TO THE HOSPITAL.  I DON'T EXPECT
HE'LL LIVE OUT THE WEEK.</i>

965
01:30:56.250 --> 01:31:00.750
- [ Groaning ]
- READY ?  AND ONE.

966
01:31:04.760 --> 01:31:09.760
[ Cheering ]

967
01:31:09.760 --> 01:31:12.770
<i>[ Machines Beeping ]</i>

968
01:31:22.780 --> 01:31:25.780
<i>[ Guard ]
THAT'S THE TROUBLE WITH
YOU NEW YORK DOPE FIENDS.</i>

969
01:31:25.780 --> 01:31:29.280
YOU GOT A ROTTEN ATTITUDE.
 YOU KNOW THAT. MAN ?

970
01:31:29.280 --> 01:31:32.290
- WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO NOW ?
- ASS TO ASS.

971
01:31:32.290 --> 01:31:36.290
<i>[ Laughing ]  ASS TO ASS !</i>

972
01:31:44.800 --> 01:31:48.800
PUT YOUR SPINELESS BACK
INTO IT !  COME ON !

973
01:31:50.810 --> 01:31:54.320
<i>READY ?
AND TWO !</i>

974
01:31:57.310 --> 01:31:59.310
<i>[ Man ]
ASS TO ASS !</i>

975
01:31:59.810 --> 01:32:03.320
<i>[ Cheering ]</i>

976
01:32:03.320 --> 01:32:06.820
<i>[ Man ]
PUT IT IN THERE !
             [ Man ]  THAT'S IT.</i>

977
01:32:06.820 --> 01:32:09.820
<i>NICE AND EASY.</i>

978
01:32:09.820 --> 01:32:13.330
<i>[ Guard ]
MASHED POTATOES.</i>

979
01:32:13.330 --> 01:32:17.330
<i>HERE'S THE CLOSE.
I NEED ONE GRAM.  BINGO.</i>

980
01:32:17.330 --> 01:32:21.830
<i>[ Man ]
DON'T GIVE UP.  DON'T GIVE UP.
MOVE IT. MOVE IT. MOVE IT !</i>

981
01:32:21.840 --> 01:32:24.350
<i>OKAY.</i>

982
01:32:24.340 --> 01:32:27.840
<i>READY ?
AND THREE !</i>

983
01:32:32.350 --> 01:32:35.350
CUM !  CUM !
  CUM !  CUM !

984
01:32:35.350 --> 01:32:37.350
CUM !  CUM !  CUM !  CUM !

985
01:32:37.350 --> 01:32:40.350
WE'RE GONNA TAKE IT OFF
AT THE SHOULDER.  LET'S MOVE IT.
OTHERWISE WE LOSE HIM !

986
01:32:40.350 --> 01:32:43.360
<i>CUM !  CUM !  CUM !  CUM !</i>

987
01:32:48.860 --> 01:32:51.860
- SAW.
- CUM !  CUM !  CUM !  CUM !

988
01:33:13.890 --> 01:33:16.890
[ Inaudible ]
MARION !

989
01:33:30.910 --> 01:33:32.920
MARION !

990
01:33:34.910 --> 01:33:36.910
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

991
01:33:36.910 --> 01:33:39.910
<i>DON'T WORRY.
YOU'RE IN A HOSPITAL.</i>

992
01:33:39.910 --> 01:33:41.910
MARION ?
<i>WHO'S THAT ?</i>

993
01:33:41.920 --> 01:33:43.930
SHE'LL BE SENT FOR.
 SHE'LL COME.

994
01:33:46.920 --> 01:33:49.420
- NO.
- NO ?

995
01:33:51.430 --> 01:33:53.440
NO. SHE WON'T.

996
01:33:53.430 --> 01:33:55.430
SHE'LL COME.

997
01:35:01.000 --> 01:35:05.010
[ Crying ]

998
01:35:58.050 --> 01:36:00.050
<i>[ Audience Applauding ]</i>

999
01:36:00.050 --> 01:36:05.060
<i>[ Tappy ]
ALL RIGHT !  WE GOT A WINNER.
[ Audience ]  WE GOT A WINNER.</i>

1000
01:36:05.060 --> 01:36:07.560
<i>[ Tappy ]
GOT A WINNER !
[ Audience ]  WE GOT A WINNER.</i>

1001
01:36:07.560 --> 01:36:10.560
<i>OUR NEXT WINNER
IS THAT DELIGHTFUL PERSONALITY.</i>

1002
01:36:10.560 --> 01:36:12.570
<i>STRAIGHT FROM
BRIGHTON BEACH. BROOKLYN.</i>

1003
01:36:13.070 --> 01:36:17.570
<i>PLEASE. GIVE A JUICY WELCOME
TO MRS. SARA GOLDFARB !</i>

1004
01:36:17.570 --> 01:36:19.570
<i>[ Cheering. Applause ]</i>

1005
01:36:19.570 --> 01:36:23.580
<i>[ Tappy ]  I'M DELIGHTED
TO TELL YOU THAT YOU HAVE
JUST WON THE GRAND PRIZE !</i>

1006
01:36:23.580 --> 01:36:25.580
OH. NO !

1007
01:36:26.080 --> 01:36:28.080
<i>LET ME TELL YOU
WHAT YOU'VE WON.</i>

1008
01:36:28.080 --> 01:36:31.080
YOUR PRIZE HAS A SWEET SMILE.
AND HIS OWN PRIVATE BUSINESS.

1009
01:36:31.090 --> 01:36:35.060
HE JUST GOT ENGAGED.
AND IS ABOUT TO GET MARRIED
THIS SUMMER.

1010
01:36:35.060 --> 01:36:39.070
WILL YOU PLEASE GIVE A WARM
AND JUICY WELCOME.
HARRY GOLDFARB !

1011
01:36:39.560 --> 01:36:42.060
<i>[ Audience ]
JUICE BY HARRY !
JUICE BY HARRY !</i>

1012
01:36:42.060 --> 01:36:45.560
<i>OOOH. HARRY'S GOT JUICE !
HARRY'S GOT JUICE !</i>

1013
01:36:45.570 --> 01:36:48.080
OOOH. HARRY !

1014
01:36:48.070 --> 01:36:51.570
- I LOVE YOU. HARRY.
- I LOVE YOU TOO. MA.

1015
01:36:51.570 --> 01:36:55.070
<i>[ Cheering. Applause ]</i>
